Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20wearing%20SteelSeries%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20wireless%20gaming%20headset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e60e4b788914e55540624%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221741%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20can%20connect%20to%20a%20console%20and%20mobile%20device%20for%20simultaneous%20wireless%20audio.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Webb%20%2F%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20several%20of%20the%20latest%20gaming%20headsets%2C%20the%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20offers%20simultaneous%20listening%20with%20wireless%202.4GHz%20audio%20and%20Bluetooth.%20We%20recommend%20using%20the%202.4GHz%20connection%20for%20gaming%20consoles%20to%20maintain%20the%20strongest%20connection%20and%20reduce%20potential%20for%20lag.%20The%20headset's%20Bluetooth%20connection%20is%20best%20used%20for%20mobile%20devices%20if%20you%20just%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nova%207X's%20wireless%202.4GHz%20connection%20relies%20on%20a%20USB-C%20dongle%20that%20you%20can%20plug%20into%20one%20of%20the%20USB%20ports%20of%20whatever%20system%20you're%20using.%20It%20has%20two%20modes%3A%20one%20for%20an%20Xbox%20connection%2C%20and%20another%20for%20standard%20USB%20audio%20devices%20including%20PlayStation%20and%20Nintendo%20Switch.%20Swapping%20the%20wireless%20mode%20is%20as%20simple%20as%20flipping%20a%20switch%20on%20the%20dongle.%20The%202.4GHz%20wireless%20range%20is%20about%2030%20to%2040%20feet%2C%20which%20is%20plenty%20for%20a%20home%20entertainment%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBluetooth%20devices%20can%20connect%20directly%20to%20the%20Nova%207X%20using%20the%20Bluetooth%20pairing%20button%20on%20the%20headset%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20sound%20delay%20compared%20to%20using%202.4GHz.%C2%A0%20However%2C%20the%20Nova%207X's%20Bluetooth%20range%20extends%20far%20beyond%20the%2040-foot%20range%20of%20the%202.4GHz%20transmitter.%20Though%20we%20weren't%20able%20to%20measure%20exactly%20how%20far%2C%20the%20Bluetooth%20range%20is%20at%20least%20several%20hundred%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nova%207X%20lasts%2035%20to%2040%20hours%20on%20a%20single%20charge%2C%20and%2015%20minutes%20of%20charging%20can%20yield%20six%20hours%20of%20play%20time.%20The%20battery%20life%20is%20comparable%20to%20other%20headsets%20in%20the%20same%20price%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20USB-C%20dongle%20functions%20just%20fine%2C%20it%20blocks%20the%20front-facing%20USB-A%20port%20of%20the%20PlayStation%205%20while%20plugged%20in%2C%20which%20feels%20like%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20oversight.%20While%20the%20PS5%20does%20have%20backwards%20facing%20USB-A%20ports%2C%20they%20can%20be%20a%20hassle%20to%20reach%20depending%20on%20your%20setup.%20Xbox%20consoles%20don't%20have%20a%20USB-C%20port%20at%20all%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20use%20the%20included%20USB-C%20to%20USB-A%20adapter%20to%20connect%20the%20dongle.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch%20dock.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20USB-C%20dongle%20can%20be%20plugged%20directly%20into%20the%20Switch%20in%20portable%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20if%20you%20do%20happen%20to%20want%20a%20wired%20connection%2C%20the%20Nova%207X%20has%20a%203.5mm%20port%20that%20can%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20device%20with%20a%20standard%20headphone%20jack%2C%20like%20the%20PlayStation%20and%20Xbox%20wireless%20controllers%2C%20and%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3EThe%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20delivers%20impressive%20sound%20quality%20and%20works%20well%20with%20spatial%20audio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221022%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20showing%20performance%20of%20the%20SteelSeries%20GG%20EQ.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e631336d588dc55ce8b59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22766%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E