ative%20of%20a%20recession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20recession%20indicators%20that%20are%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20flashing%2C%20but%20even%20if%20they%20do%20flash%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-2024-sp500-test-record-highs-profits-rise-2023-11%5C%22%3Estock%20market%20investors%20can%20rest%20easy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20these%20economic%20indicators%20are%20being%20driven%20by%20different%20factors%20today%20than%20they%20were%20in%20the%20past%20when%20they%20correctly%20predicted%20an%20imminent%20recession%2C%20according%20to%20Carson%20Group's%20global%20macro%20strategist%20Sonu%20Varghese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESahm%20Rule%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20recession%20indicator%20is%20the%20Sahm%20Rule%2C%20which%20flashes%20when%20the%20three-month%20average%20of%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20rises%2050%20basis%20points%20above%20its%20low%20over%20the%20previous%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20rose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-unemployment-rate-recession-outlook-labor-market-wages-federal-reserve-2023-11%5C%22%3Eto%203.9%25%2C%20up%2050%20basis%20points%20from%20its%20cycle%20low%20of%203.4%25%20in%20April%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20three-month%20average%20is%20now%2033%20basis%20points%20above%20its%20low%2C%20just%2017%20basis%20points%20away%20from%20triggering%20the%20Sahm%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indicator%20was%20founded%20by%20former%20Fed%20economist%20Claudia%20Sahm%2C%20and%20when%20it%20flashes%20the%20chances%20of%20a%20recession%20rise%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221137%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sahm%20Rule%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e86f93cc84b4dfa0055aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22805%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYCharts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20highly%20accurate.%20Going%20back%20to%20the%201970's%20every%20single%20recession%20hits%20it%20and%20doesn't%20hit%20outside%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2023%2F11%2F10%2Fsigns-of-a-recession-may-be-on-the-horizon-says-fmr-fed-economist-claudia-sahm.html%3F%26qsearchterm%3DClaudia%2520Sahm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClaudia%20Sahm%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Friday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20once%20unemployment%20starts%20rising%2C%20it%20often%20becomes%20a%20feedback%20loop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20a%20small%20increase%20in%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20can%20be%20really%20bad%20news%2C%20because%20it%20keeps%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Varghese%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20rise%20in%20unemployment%20is%20being%20driven%20by%20an%20increase%20in%20labor%20supply%2C%20due%20in%20part%20to%20higher%20immigration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20labor%20force%20has%20been%20growing%20at%20a%201.5%25-2%25%20annualized%20pace%2C%20nearly%20double%20the%20pre-pandemic%20pace%2C%20he%20said%2C%20meaning%20new%20workers%20are%20joining%20the%20labor%20pool%20faster%20than%20they%20can%20find%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20labor%20supply%20increasing%2C%20we're%20not%20sure%20the%20Sahm%20rule%2C%20even%20if%20it%20triggers%2C%20would%20really%20be%20indicative%20of%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Varghese%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%20enough%2C%20Sahm%20is%20in%20agreement%20with%20Varghese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20echoed%20his%20point%20about%20labor%20supply%2C%20saying%20a%20burst%20of%20people%20re-entered%20the%20workforce%20this%20year%2C%20outpacing%20the%20rate%20of%20job%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20base%20case%20is%20that%20we%20avoid%20a%20recession.%20My%20base%20case%20is%20also%20that%20the%20Sahm%20rule%20breaks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EUninverting%20yield%20curve%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20recessionary%20indicator%20occurs%20when%20an%20inverted%20yield%20curve%20uninverts%20back%20into%20positive%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20gotten%20closer%20to%20happening%20in%20recent%20weeks%20as%20the%202-%20and%2010-year%20US%20Treasury%20yields%20converged.%20The%20spread%20between%20them%20was%20as%20wide%20as%20-1.06%25%20in%20July%20but%20got%20down%20to%20just%20-0.13%25%20in%20late%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yield%20curve%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e87b936d588dc55ceb677%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22805%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYCharts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20recessions%20have%20occurred%20shortly%20after%20the%20yield%20curve%20uninverted%20back%20into%20positive%20territory.%20But%20Varghese%20is%20unmoved%20by%20this%20recession%20indicator%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%20that's%20happened%20as%20the%20Fed%20quickly%20lowers%20short-term%20rates%20amid%20a%20slowing%20economy.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20spread%20is%20narrowing%20because%20long-term%20yields%20are%20rising%2C%20on%20the%20back%20of%20stronger-than-expected%20economic%20growth%20prospects%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dynamic%20was%20on%20full%20display%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-news-today-goldilocks-jobs-report-biggest-weekly-gain-2023-11%5C%22%3Ewhen%20bond%20yields%20moved%20lower%20after%20a%20weak%20October%20jobs%20report%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlighting%20that%20yields%20have%20been%20driven%20by%20economic%20growth%20expectations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll-in%2C%20the%20potential%20flashing%20of%20these%20two%20recession%20indicators%20might%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20knock%20down%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20broader%20economy%2C%20as%20increasing%20labor%20supply%20and%20solid%20economic%20growth%20are%20the%20driving%20factors%20behind%20the%20indicators%2C%20not%20economic%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-indicators-stock-market-outlook-yield-curve-sahm-jobless-rate-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699647576000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60d2315ac097fe00185a24f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Frecession-indicators-stock-market-outlook-yield-curve-sahm-jobless-rate-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWith%20labor%20supply%20increasing%2C%20we're%20not%20sure%20the%20Sahm%20rule%2C%20even%20if%20it%20triggers%2C%20would%20be%20indicative%20of%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Sonu%20Varghese%20told%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ethics%20panel%20exceeded%20brief%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699647575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105133765%2Cimgsize-40408.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fethics-panel-exceeded-brief-mahua-moitra%2Farticleshow%2F105133761.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ethics%20Committee%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20sent%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Speaker%20recommending%20the%20disqualification%20of%20TMC%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20'cash%20for%20query'%20scam.%20Moitra%20denies%20any%20involvement%20in%20the%20alleged%20cash%20or%20gift%20transactions%20and%20claims%20that%20the%20committee%20exceeded%20its%20mandate%20by%20recommending%20her%20expulsion.