e%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAm%20Sewak%2C%20Not%20In%20Race%20For%20Chief%20Minister%26quot%3B%3A%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20has%20said%20he%20is%20not%20in%20any%20race%20to%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Minister%20said%20the%20question%20of%20him%20running%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20does%20not%20arise%20as%20he%20has%20always%20been%20a%20party%20worker%20and%20will%20remain%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20people%20vying%20for%20power%2C%20they%20have%20groups%2C%20they%20scheme%20to%20become%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20and%20before%20elections%20Congress%20has%20some%20eight%20leaders%20claiming%20to%20be%20Chief%20Minister.%20BJP%20is%20a%20party%20of%20workers.%20We%20are%20all%20karyakartas%2C%20and%20will%20remain%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20told%20NDTV%20inside%20his%20campaign%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20fighting%20the%20election%20under%20Prime%20Minister's%20leadership...%20I%20am%20not%20in%20this%20race%20(for%20Chief%20Minister's%20post).%20I%20am%20a%20%3Cem%3Esewak%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20am%20not%20in%20the%20race%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20on%20November%202%20had%20said%20something%20similar%20about%20not%20including%20the%20Scindia%20family%20in%20the%20race%20for%20the%20chair.%20%26quot%3BNever%20include%20the%20Scindia%20family%20in%20the%20race%20for%20the%20chair%20(referring%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post).%20The%20Scindia%20family%20works%20day%20and%20night%20with%20a%20passion%20for%20development%2C%20progress%20and%20public%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20hit%20back%20at%20his%20former%20party%2C%20Congress%2C%20over%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20punched%20holes%20in%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20which%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20gain%20support%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20OBC%20factor%3F%20Congress%20thinks%20the%20people%20can't%20see%20through%20them%3F%20There%20are%2027%20OBC%20ministers%20in%20Modi%20ji's%20cabinet%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress's%20G%20(guarantee)%20is%20not%20only%202G%2C%20they%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20do%205G%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20scam%20in%20allotting%202G%20spectrum%20under%20the%20UPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20whatever%20abuses%20the%20Congress%20gives%20me.%20I%20have%20no%20grudge%20against%20the%20Congress.%20Whatever%20abuses%20the%20Congress%20may%20say%20to%20me%2C%20they%20even%20abused%20my%20family.%20The%20person%20who%20gave%20his%20life%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20my%20respected%20father%2C%20He%20was%20martyred%20while%20going%20to%20the%20Congress%20rally.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20when%20I%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%20or%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Congress.%20Are%20you%20reading%20a%20new%20history%3F%20Are%20you%20reading%20the%20history%20of%20the%20British%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20he%20was%20sure%20the%20BJP%20would%20form%20a%20full-majority%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20will%20vote%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20November%2017%3B%20counting%20is%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699640640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F6ov9bglo_jyotiraditya-scindia_625x300_10_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-2023-am-sewak-not-in-race-for-chief-minister-says-jyotiradtya-scindia-to-ndtv-4565722%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20has%20said%20he%20is%20not%20in