%20in%20Kerala%20on%20Friday%20sentenced%20a%2063-year-old%20man%20to%20109%20years%20of%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20for%20raping%20a%20minor%20girl%20whom%20he%20had%20adopted%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fast-track%20special%20court%20in%20Adoor%20in%20this%20southern%20district%20of%20the%20state%20awarded%20the%20punishment%20to%20Thomas%20Samuel%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Kurampala%20in%20Pandalam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20imposed%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%206.25%20lakh%20on%20the%20convict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20A%20Sameer%20ordered%20that%20if%20the%20fine%20is%20not%20paid%2C%20Samuel%20would%20have%20to%20undergo%20an%20additional%20imprisonment%20of%20three%20years%20and%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ordered%20that%20the%20fine%20amount%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20victim%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20girl%20hailing%20from%20neighbouring%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20police%20statement%20said%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convict%20will%20have%20to%20serve%20a%20total%20of%2020%20years%20in%20prison%20as%20his%20sentence%20will%20run%20concurrently%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20some%20years%20ago%20the%20girl%20was%20staying%20on%20the%20veranda%20of%20a%20local%20shop%20here%20with%20her%20two%20siblings%20and%20paternal%20grandmother%20after%20their%20parents%20abandoned%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20learning%20about%20their%20plight%2C%20the%20child%20welfare%20panel%20took%20steps%20to%20ensure%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20that%2C%20three%20local%20families%20adopted%20the%20three%20children%2C%20promising%20them%20a%20safe%20and%20secure%20life.%20The%20victim%20was%20adopted%20by%20Samuel%20and%20his%20wife%20who%20had%20no%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20girl%20reached%20their%20home%2C%20the%20man%20allegedly%20started%20misbehaving%20with%20her%20and%20subjected%20her%20to%20cruel%20sexual%20as