20events%20unfolded%20in%20Sri%20Lankan%20cricket%20following%20the%20team's%20disappointing%20run%20in%20the%20ongoing%20World%20Cup%20in%20India.%20Sri%20Lanka%20could%20manage%20only%20two%20wins%20from%20nine%20games%20and%20are%20out%20of%20the%20semifinals%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20opposition%20party%20leader%20Sajith%20Premadasa%20moved%20the%20resolution%20titled%20'the%20removal%20of%20the%20corrupt%20SLC%20(Sri%20Lanka%20Cricket)%20management'%20which%20was%20seconded%20by%20the%20senior%20government%20minister%20Nimal%20Siripala%20de%20Silva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliament's%20approval%20came%20two%20days%20after%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20restored%20the%20SLC%20management%20headed%20by%20Shammi%20Silva%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Sports%20Minister%20Roshan%20Ranasinghe%20sacked%20the%20SLC%20management%20and%20appointed%20former%20World%20Cup-winning%20captain%20Arjuna%20Ranatunga%20as%20head%20of%20a%20seven-member%20interim%20committee%20to%20govern%20the%20cricket%20board%20before%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20restored%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20parliament%20was%20debating%20the%20resolution%2C%20police%20protection%20was%20provided%20to%20SLC%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20hundred%20people%20had%20turned%20up%20near%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20SLC%20headquarters%20calling%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criticism%20of%20the%20national%20team's%20performance%20grew%20louder%20when%20Sri%20Lanka%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%2055%20in%20the%20run%20chase%20against%20India%20in%20Mumbai.%20Sri%20Lanka%20had%20also%20lost%20badly%20to%20India%20in%20the%20preceding%20Asia%20Cup%20where%20they%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%2050%20in%20the%20final%20played%20on%20September%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20the%20ICC%20handed%20a%20suspension%20to%20a%20full%20member%20was%20back%20in%202021%20when%20Zimbabwe%20Cricket%20was%2