22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fegypts-stumbling-economy-faces-new-pressures-from-gaza-crisis%2Famp_articleshow%2F105130961.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Only%20Disturbing%20Part%20In%20The%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Row%20Is%20His%20Apology%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20about%20sex%2C%20except%20sex.%20Sex%20is%20about%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20the%20author%20and%20enfant%20terrible%20of%20Victorian-era%20London%2C%20Oscar%20Wilde%2C%20ever%20made%20the%20above%20statement%2C%20psychoanalysts%20across%20decades%20have%20largely%20agreed%20with%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20would%20have%20thought%2C%20however%2C%20that%20even%20talking%20about%20sex%20would%20engender%20power%20play%20in%20India's%20political%20stadium%20where%20there%20are%20more%20misses%20than%20hits%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20speech%20on%20sex%20education%20and%20population%20has%20created%20an%20entirely%20unnecessary%20furore%20where%20issues%20like%20reproductive%20health%20and%20fertility%20rate%20are%20being%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20usual%20balderdash%20on%20propriety%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20that%20dangerous%20thing%20called%20honour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20remains%20in%20the%20unenviable%20top%20spot%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20maternal%20and%20infant%20mortality%20rates.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20UN%20report%20indicated%20plateauing%20of%20gains%20made%20in%20reducing%20deaths%20related%20to%20maternal%20health.%20The%20most%20recent%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS-5)%20gives%20an%20insight%20into%20this%20depressing%20trend.%20Only%2010%25%20Indian%20women%20can%20exercise%20autonomy%20over%20their%20own%20health.%20The%20survey%20also%20suggests%20a%20disturbing%20mind-set%3A%2011%25%20women%20find%20marital%20violence%20acceptable%20on%20account%20of%20the%20husband's%20sexual%20demands%20not%20being%20met%20by%20the%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20going%20ballistic%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%20giving%20graphic%20details%20of%20heterosexual%20intercourse%20and%20the%20pull-out%20method%20for%20birth%20control%20-%20using%20only%20euphemisms%20-%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20are%20probably%20being%20ostriches.%20When%20you%20are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%2C%20propriety%20in%20language%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20the%20mainstay%20of%20any%20argument.%20And%20let%20us%20not%20kid%20ourselves%20anyway.%20All%20our%20cuss%20words%20revolve%20around%20women's%20genitalia%20and%20crude%20phrases%20describing%20sexual%20acts%2C%20often%20forced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20proven%20conclusively%20that%20lack%20of%20sexual%20literacy%20is%20the%20main%20source%20of%20several%20sexual%20hazards%20including%20STDs%20and%20unintended%20pregnancies.%20In%20a%20culture%20where%20not%20only%20women's%20sexual%20pleasure%20and%20desires%20are%20marginalised%20but%20also%20their%20health%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20sexual%20literacy%2C%20understanding%20the%20role%20of%20language%20is%20germane%20to%20the%20formulation%20of%20comprehensive%20health%20and%20population%20control%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeath%20is%20the%20bane%20of%20respectability.%20What%20we%20cannot%20define%20and%20convey%20within%20the%20paradigms%20of%20respectability%20often%20kills%20us.%20Are%20we%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20price%20this%20hefty%20for%20vague%20concepts%20like%20honour%20and%20respectability%3F%20Harmful%20cultural%20practices%20persist%20and%20prevail%20because%20we%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20glorifying%20victimhood.%20Why%20it%20should%20be%20so%2C%20is%20anybody's%20guess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nitish%20Kumar%20talked%20about%20the%20pull-out%20method%20and%20emphasised%20the%20role%20of%20women's%20education%2C%20he%20underscored%20women's%20agency%20over%20their%20own%20bodies.%20Is%20this%20what%20irked%20the%20honour%20brigade%3F%20Clearly%2C%20an%20unhealthy%2C%20or%20even%20dead%2C%20woman%20is%20better%20than%20an%20empowered%20woman%20for%20them.%20Nothing%20is%20scarier%20than%20an%20autonomous%2C%20sexually%20autonomous%2C%20woman%20to%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20patriarchal%20status%20quo.%20Any%20means%20need%20to%20be%20employed%20to%20subjugate%2C%20demonise%2C%20and%20otherise%20her.%20The%20tools%20that%20come%20in%20handy%20for%20this%20purpose%20are%20moral%20and%20cultural%20outrage.%20Women%20themselves%20are%20conned%20into%20believing%20that%20their%20lives%20and%20choices%20are%20second%20to%20the%20socio-cultural%20mores.%20It%20is%20the%20same%20mindset%20that%20perpetuated%20practices%20like%20the%20sati%20in%20the%20past.%20And%20continues%20to%20lead%20women%20astray%20from%20the%20path%20of%20self-preservation%20and%20prioritisation.%20It%20works%20very%20well%20for%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20honouring%20a%20specific%20local%20moral%20order%2C%20most%20women%20are%20trapped%20in%20a%20purgatory%20of%20sorts.%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20words%2C%20even%20if%20he%20didn't%20intend%20them%20the%20way%20they%20were%20received%20-%20and%20for%20which%20he%20eventually%20extended%20an%20unnecessary%20apology%20-%20attempted%20to%20free%20women%20from%20the%20said%20trap.%20Employing%20language%20that%20is%20at%20once%20familiar%20and%20earthy%20to%20drive%20the%20basics%20of%20sexual%20health%20and%20autonomy%2C%20he%20took%20a%20remarkable%20stride%20in%20the%20space%20of%20women's%20health%20and%20empowerment.%20Of%20course%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20be%20shamed%20for%20it%20by%20trivialising%20and%20vulgarising%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20disturbing%20aspect%20about%20the%20entire%20episode%20is%20that%20he%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20apologise.%20It%20shows%20that%20even%20the%20best%20intentions%20around%20women's%20empowerment%20need%20to%20be%20couched%20in%20the%20notions%20of%20respect%20and%20acceptability.%20The%20bogey%20of%20respectability%20is%20the%20most%20difficult%20to%20get%20rid%20of.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20electoral%20politics%2C%20nobody%20wants%20to%20risk%20anything.%20This%20is%20tragic%20in%20all%20possible%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20will%20it%20take%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20human%20being%2C%20and%20not%20an%20inanimate%20receptacle%20and%20repository%20of%20honour%3F%20What%20will%20it%20take%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20flesh%20and%20blood%20entity%20that%20needs%20as%20much%20attention%20to%20the%20physicality%20of%20her%20existence%2C%20away%20from%20vagueness%3F%20Those%20who%20are%20quoting%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20iterations%20as%20an%20assault%20on%20women's%20honour%20are%2C%20essentially%2C%20condemning%20women%20to%20a%20state%20of%20ephemeral%20nothingness.%20This%20cannot%20be%20allowed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20poet%20Mahmoud%20Darwish%20said%20it%20better%20than%20many.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20tire%3Cbr%3E%5Cnfrom%20the%20moon's%20feminine%20cycle%3Cbr%3E%5Cnand%20my%20guitar%20falls%20ill%3Cbr%3E%5Cnstring%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%20string%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20am%20a%20woman%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cnno%20more%3Cbr%3E%5Cnand%20no%20less!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699629840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Faevometo_nitish-kumar-1200_625x300_08_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fonly-disturbing-part-in-the-nitish-kumar-row-is-his-apology-4565211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Who%20would%20have%20thought%2C%20however%2C%20that%20even%20talking%20about%20sex%20would%20engender%20power%20play%20in%20India's%20political%20stadium%20where%20there%20are%20more%20misses%20than%20hits%3F%22%