00%20patients%20and%20the%20initial%20police%20investigation%20shows%20that%20at%20least%20200%20of%20them%20were%20sub-standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20advocate%20Mohammed%20Tahir's%20wife%20Reshma%20Begum%20started%20feeling%20uneasy%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20University%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20Saifai.%20A%20temporary%20pacemaker%20was%20implanted%20in%20her%20and%20Mr%20Tahir%20was%20urged%20to%20get%20a%20permanent%20one%20implanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplications%20persisted%20after%20the%20surgery%2C%20and%20Reshma%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Delhi%20as%20well%2C%20but%20she%20could%20not%20be%20saved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEtawah%20resident%20Mohammad%20Naseem%20had%20also%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife%20Najma%20Parveen%20lost%20her%20life%20due%20to%20Dr%20Saraf's%20negligence.%20He%20had%20claimed%20Dr%20Saraf%20took%20Rs%204%20lakh%20for%20an%20implantable%20cardioverter-defibrillator%20(ICD)%20and%20then%20implanted%20it%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20the%20medical%20superintendent%20of%20the%20institute%2C%20Dr%20Adesh%20Kumar%2C%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20Dr%20Saraf%20and%20the%20police%20registered%20a%20case%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20arrested%20Dr%20Sameer%20Saraf%2C%20a%20cardiologist%20at%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20University%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20Saifai.%20He%20faces%20various%20allegations%2C%20including%20overcharging%20patients%2C%20financial%20irregularities%20and%20using%20substandard%20medical%20devices%2C%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20PTI%20quoted%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Santosh%20Kumar%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20now%20probing%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20larger%20nexus%20involved%20and%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20which%20company%20had%20supplied%20the%20fake%20pacemakers%20to%20Dr%20Saraf.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699627920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-09%2Fdoctor-generic_650x400_81442427279.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-doctor-implanted-sub-standard-pacemakers-over-200-patients-affected-cops-4565073%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20cardiologist%20from%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20who%20prioritised%20money%20over%20people's%20health%20and%20allegedly%20implanted%20sub-standard%20pacemakers%20in%20his%20patients%20while%20charging%20as%20much%20as%20nine%20times%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20standard%20one%2C%20has%20been%20arrested.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-doctor-implanted-sub-standard-pacemakers-over-200-patients-affected-cops-4565073%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-doctor-implanted-sub-standard-pacemakers-over-200-patients-affected-cops-4565073%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-doctor-implanted-sub-standard-pacemakers-over-200-patients-affected-cops-4565073%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAS%20Coaching%20Centre%20Fined%20Rs%205%20Lakh%20for%20Misleading%20Ads%20With%20Toppers%3A%20Red%20Flags%20You%20Should%20Check%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Consumer%20Protection%20Authority%20(CCPA)%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20on%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20(KSG)%2C%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20India%2C%20on%20account%20of%20unfair%20trade%20practices%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F158493%2Fadvertising-misleading-ads-legal-recourse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emisleading%20advertising%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20action%20comes%20after%20observing%20various%20civil%20services%20exam%20coaching%20centres%20which%20post%20advertisements%20claiming%20successful%20candidates%20to%20be%20their%20students.%20These%20institutes%20use%20pictures%20and%20names%20of%20toppers%20without%20indicating%20the%20length%20of%20the%20course%2C%20the%20fees%20paid%20or%20the%20course%20opted%20to%20lure%20prospective%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20advertisement%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20valid%20and%20not%20deceitful%20when%20it%20does%20not%20mislead%20consumers%20by%20exaggerating%20the%20usefulness%20of%20the%20products%20or%20services%2C%20says%20the%20consumer%20affairs%20ministry.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKSG%20was%20found%20making%20false%20claims%20such%20as%20682%20out%20of%20933%20selected%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20students%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20from%20KSG.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20DG%20(Investigation)%20CCPA%20was%20asked%20for%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20into%20the%20matters%20and%20it%20was%20found%20in%20the%20investigation%20report%20that%20out%20of%20682%2C%20only%20eight%20successful%20candidates%20took%20guidance%20for%20additional%20courses%20and%20that%20too%20in%20previous%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20those%208%2C%20the%20five%20toppers%20only%20took%20mock%20interview%20programmes%20from%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20which%20were%20free%20of%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20being%20lured%20by%20such%20scams%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20red%20flags%20to%20spot%20as%20suggested%20by%20Aakarsh%20Agarwal%2C%20a%20motivational%20speaker%2C%20lawyer%2C%20and%20financial%20guide%20on%20Quora.%20Aakarsh%20has%20over%204%20lakh%20views%20on%20his%20profile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Do%20not%20fall%20for%20unrealistic%20success%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coaching%20centre%20claiming%20a%2099%20percent%20or%20100%20percent%20success%20rate%20is%20a%20big%20red%20flag%20according%20to%20Aakarsh.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20success%20rates%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20a%20number%20of%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20the%20difficulty%20level%20of%20the%20exam%20and%20the%20individual%20abilities%20of%20the%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Beware%20of%20fake%20reviews%20and%20testimonials%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkarsh%20says%20that%20if%20there%20are%20too%20many%20good%20reviews%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262120%2Fjharkhand-free-online-classes-zoom-youtube-paathshala-upsc-examinations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20coaching%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20they%20might%20be%20fake.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20try%20to%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20reviews%20by%20checking%20if%20they%20are%20from%20real%20people%20and%20if%20they%20have%20similar%20language%20or%20writing%20styles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Ask%20for%20result%20verification%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suggests%20asking%20for%20verification%20of%20all%20the%20good%20results%20the%20institute%20is%20claiming.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20provide%20proof%20of%20their%20students%E2%80%99%20success%2C%20such%20as%20exam%20scores%20or%20certificates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20red%20flag.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20upon%20request%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Check%20for%20accreditation%20or%20certification%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20red%20flag%20that%20he%20suggests%20that%20everyone%20should%20watch%20out%20for%20is%20certification.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20accredited%20or%20certified%20by%20a%20recognised%20organisation%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20they%20are%20not%20meeting%20certain%20standards%20or%20regulations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Lack%20of%20transparency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20transparent%20about%20its%20teaching%20methods%2C%20course%20materials%2C%20or%20success%20rates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20to%20prospective%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakarsh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699627832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Searching%20for%20the%20best%20UPSC%20coaching%20institute%3F%20The%20Central%20Consumer%20Protection%20Authority%20(CCPA)%20has%20just%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20Lakh%20on%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20(KSG)%20for%20misleading%20ads%20with%20IAS%20toppers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334054%2Fccpa-fines-khan-study-group-how-to-choose-upsc-coaching-centre-in-delhi-ias-toppers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Have%20A%20Plan%26quot%3B%3A%20Babar's%20Clear%20Take%20On%20Pakistan's%20WC%202023%20Semis%20Scenarios%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20cricket%20team%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-