%3EThe%20bench%20said%20it%20was%20modifying%20its%20order%20of%20November%206.%20%26quot%3BThe%20time%20to%20burst%20crackers%20shall%20be%20limited%20from%208%20pm%20to%2010%20pm%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20prevalent%20situation%2C%20it%20does%20not%20deem%20it%20appropriate%20to%20modify%20another%20direction%20in%20its%20November%206%20order%20which%20had%20banned%20the%20entry%20of%20vehicles%20transporting%20debris%20in%20the%20city%20but%20permitted%20vehicles%20carrying%20construction%20materials%20to%20ply%20if%20they%20were%20fully%20covered%2C%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20other%20directions%20of%20the%20November%206%20order%20shall%20continue%20to%20operate%20till%20November%2019%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20November%2019%2C%20concerned%20municipal%20corporations%20shall%20decide%20whether%20vehicles%20carrying%20debris%20should%20be%20allowed%20after%20considering%20the%20AQI%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20of%20pollution%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20ascertained%2C%20it%20said%2C%20while%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20a%20study%20by%20experts%20to%20understand%20the%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20there%20any%20study%20as%20to%20what%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20this%20pollution...is%20it%20only%20dust%20or%20is%20there%20any%20chemical%20component%20in%20it%3F%20Because%20we%20are%20seeing%20many%20hospitals%20flooded%20with%20patients%20with%20respiratory%20illness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20including%20one%20taken%20up%20by%20it%20on%20its%20own%20(%60suo%20motu')%20concerning%20the%20rising%20air%20pollution%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20further%20on%20December%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20it%20noted%20that%20the%20problem%20of%20air%20pollution%20would%20recur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20is%20a%20study%20by%20experts%20to%20go%20into%20causes%20and%20also%20measures%20to%20mitigate%20the%20pollution.%20We%20are%20not%20experts%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20constant%20monitoring%20mechanism%20was%20also%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20General%20Birendra%20Saraf%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20state%20government%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20government%2C%20right%20from%20the%20level%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%2C%20has%20been%20making%20its%20sincerest%20efforts%2C%20and%20the%20AQI%20levels%20in%20the%20city%20have%20reached%20satisfactory%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20commented%20that%20this%20was%20because%20of%20the%20spells%20of%20rain%20that%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20received%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20the%20rains%2C%26quot%3B%20CJ%20Upadhyaya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20all%20that%20the%20government%20and%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20have%20been%20doing%20is%20fine%20and%20good%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20you%20are%20not%20doing%20any%20favour%20on%20anyone.%20That%20is%20your%20duty%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20counsel%20Milind%20Sathe%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20BMC%2C%20said%20the%20civic%20body%20has%20been%20implementing%20the%20guidelines%20issued%20following%20its%20March%202023%20pollution%20mitigation%20action%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civic%20body's%20flying%20squads%20have%20so%20far%20visited%201%2C623%20construction%20and%20other%20sites%2C%20of%20which%201%2C065%20were%20issued%20notices%20for%20not%20complying%20with%20the%20pollution%20control%20norms%20and%20guidelines%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20number%20of%20sites%20flouting%20the%20norms%20was%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20data%20speaks%20a%20lot.%20This%20shows%20that%20everything%20is%20not%20as%20rosy%20as%20the%20picture%20the%20BMC%20is%20trying%20to%20paint%2C%26quot%3B%20CJ%20Upadhyaya%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20figures%20provided%20by%20the%20BMC%20itself%20speak%20volumes%20about%20the%20alarming%20state%20of%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20a%20committee%20with%20experts%20and%20said%20the%20courts%20should%20be%20only%20for%20adjudication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20this%20is%20the%20job%20of%20the%20executive%20that%20has%20been%20thrust%20upon%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20banned%20chemical%20firecrackers%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20there%20any%20mechanism%20to%20check%20this%20at%20the%20manufacturing%20level%20itself%3F%20Or%20is%20there%20any%20mechanism%20to%20check%20this%20in%20the%20market%20where%20firecrackers%20are%20sold%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%20had%2C%20on%20November%206%2C%20formed%20a%20committee%20comprising%20experts%20on%20environment%20and%20air%20pollution.%20On%20Friday%2C%20it%20added%20a%20retired%20bureaucrat%20as%20its%20third%20member.%20All%20municipal%20corporations%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20Metropolitan%20Region%20will%20give%20it%20daily%20reports%20and%20it%20will%20submit%20the%20court%20a%20weekly%20report%2C%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699627380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fngo445no_mumbai-pollution-november-7-2023_625x300_07_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fair-pollution-bombay-high-court-modifies-firecracker-order-for-mumbai-lets-not-become-