20has%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20was%20he%20who%20had%20taken%20action%20in%20this%20case.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20relates%20to%20the%20sale%20of%20a%2019-acre%20plot%20of%20land%20in%20the%20city's%20southwest%20that%20was%20bought%20in%202018%20by%20the%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20sale%20price%20of%20Rs%2041.52%20crore%20was%20decided%20by%20the%20then%20district%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20raised%20to%20Rs%20353.79%20crore%20by%20Hemant%20Kumar%2C%20the%20then%20South%20West%20Delhi%20district%20magistrate.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20was%20later%20suspended%20and%20his%20order%20set%20aside.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Indian%20Express%2C%20the%20complainant%20has%20argued%20the%20higher%20price%20ordered%20to%20be%20paid%20by%20the%20NHAI%20to%20one%20of%20the%20landowners%20was%20manipulated%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Secretary.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landowner%20who%20was%20to%20receive%20the%20higher%20price%20-%20Subhash%20Chand%20Kathuria%20-%20is%20directly%20related%20to%20one%20Aman%20Sarin%2C%20who%20is%20the%20promoter%20of%20realty%20firm%20Anant%20Raaj%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarin%20has%20alleged%20links%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary's%20son%20Karan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Wire%2C%20Karan%20is%20a%20Director%20at%20another%20real%20estate%20firm%20-%20one%20called%20Big%20Town%20Properties%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20which%20shares%20the%20same%20postal%20and%20email%20addresses%20as%20Anant%20Raaj%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20in%20June%2C%20this%20matter%20was%20brought%20to%20Mr%20Kumar's%20attention.%20The%20Chief%20Secretary%20directed%20Delhi's%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20-%20which%20he%20heads%20-%20to%20probe%20the%20case.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20September%2C%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%20and%20departmental%20action%20were%20recommended%20against%20Hemant%20Kumar%20-%20the%20district%20magistrate%20concerned.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20have%20commented%20on%20this%20row%3B%20Mr%20Chadha%20has%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bshocking%26quot%3B%20and%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BLast%20year...%20serious%20questions%20(were%20raised)%20about%20Chief%20Secretary%20Mr%20Naresh%20Kumar.%20Now%20this...%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20latest%20corruption%20allegation%20comes%20as%20the%20AAP%20is%20locked%20in%20a%20battle%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20controls%20the%20centre%20and%20-%20thanks%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%20-%20transfer%20of%20bureaucrats%20and%20employees%20in%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699626600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F5pl99oao_chief-secretary-naresh-kumar_625x300_18_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorruption-charge-against-top-delhi-official-arvind-kejriwal-seeks-probe-4565020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20office%20has%20received%20a%20corruption%20complaint%20against%20Chief%20Secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20and%20the%20complaint%20has%20been%20forwarded%20to%20Vigilance%20Minister%20Atishi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorruption-charge-against-top-delhi-official-arvind-kejriwal-seeks-probe-4565020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorruption-charge-against-top-delhi-official-arvind-