-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Shami%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20top%20performers%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20and%20their%20performances%20have%20been%20critical%20to%20maintain%20their%20side's%20unbeaten%20run%20till%20now.%20While%20Bumrah%20has%20taken%2015%20wickets%20till%20now%2C%20Shami%20is%20leading%20the%20pack%20of%20Indian%20bowlers%20with%2016%20scalps%20in%20far%20less%20games.%20Former%20India%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20asked%20to%20pick%20between%20the%20two%20pacers%20as%20the%20top%20choice%20for%20becoming%20the%20highest%20wicket-taker%20for%20India%20in%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20and%20he%20had%20a%20clear%20reasoning%20behind%20his%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Shami%20because%20people%20do%20not%20take%20on%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%20He's%20too%20good%20a%20bowler%20for%20an%20opposition%20to%20take%20him%20on.%20A%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20the%20best%20bowler%20will%20not%20have%20the%20most%20number%20of%20wickets.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20the%20opposition%20thinks%20let's%20see%20him%20off.%20If%20you%20observe%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20initial%20spell%2C%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20take%20him%20on.%20A%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20the%20team's%20best%20bowler%20would%20have%20a%20very%20good%20economy%20rate%2C%20but%20he%20won't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20wickets%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said%20in%20an%20interaction%20with%20Sportskeeda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20Shami%20%5Bwill%20take%20more%20wickets%5D%2C%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20that%20opposition%20will%20look%20to%20attack%20h