onomic%20Framework%20(IPEF)%20ministerial%20meeting%20and%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20attend%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20Summit%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20his%20arrival%2C%20the%20minister%20is%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20with%20Tesla%20chief%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20plans%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20between%20Goyal%20and%20Musk%20will%20stress%20Tesla's%20plans%20of%20foraying%20into%20India%20and%20the%20manufacture%20of%20more%20Tesla%20components%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meeting%20comes%20almost%20four%20months%20after%20Musk%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20New%20York%20City%20and%20expressed%20his%20interest%20in%20making%20significant%20investments%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20will%20also%20interact%20with%20two%20top%20US%20officials%2C%20including%20US%20Secretary%20of%20Commerce%20Gina%20Raimondo%20and%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20(USTR)%20Katherine%20Tai%2C%20to%20strengthen%20the%20partnership%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20and%20strengthen%20trade%20and%20economic%20ties.%20The%20Commerce%20minister%20will%20also%20interact%20with%20ministers%20from%20other%20IPEF%20partner%20countries%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20IPEF%20ministerial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20and%20Raimondo%20will%20also%20jointly%20participate%20in%20the%20United%20States-India%20Business%20Council%20(USIBC)%20event%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20economic%20leaders%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20be%20talking%20in%20that%20meeting%20with%20a%20number%20of%20companies%2C%20USIBC%20members%2C%20but%20also%20with%20startups%20in%20the%20innovation%20space%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20to%20foster%20even%20more%20unicorn-like%20startups%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20India%2Cl%26quot%3B%20Atul%20Keshap%2C%20president%2C%20USIBC%2C%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAPEC%20in%20San%20Francisco%20will%20see%20some%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20world%20leaders%20and%20business%20executives%20convene%2C%20discuss%20vital%20issues%2C%20and%20collectively%20shape%20the%20trajectory%20of%20a%20region%20that%20holds%20immense%20importance%20for%20global%20prosperity%2C%20stability%2C%20and%20sustainability.%20The%20summit%20programme%20will%20highlight%20the%20potential%20of%20collaboration%20and%20fresh%20thinking%20to%20build%20the%20future%20through%20a%20focus%20on%20Sustainability%2C%20Inclusion%2C%20Resilience%2C%20and%20Innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20summit%20will%20also%20bring%20together%2020%20leading%20CEO's%20representing%20companies%20such%20as%20Microsoft%20Pfizer%2C%20Uber%2C%20Citibank%2C%20Fedex%2C%20Exxon%20Mobil%20Corp%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20many%20of%20which%2C%20have%20deep%20economic%20interests%20in%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20region%20and%20China%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20for%20the%20United%20States%20to%20invite%20India%20to%20this%20APEC%20summit%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20to%20me%20is%20a%20really%20big%20deal.%20India%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20APEC%2C%20although%20it%20asked%20to%20become%20a%20member%20back%20in%201991%20when%20APEC%20was%20formed.%20And%20I%20think%20this%20administration%20is%20actually%20putting%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20into%20trying%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20India%20to%20include%20it%20in%20our%20trade%20efforts%20around%20the%20world.%20Look%20at%20the%20Indopacific%20economic%20framework%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20diplomat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20summit%2C%20Goyal%20will%20have%20a%20brief%20informal%20interaction%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20the%20former%20will%20also%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20APEC%20group%20photo.%20Biden%20will%20also%20welcome%20other%20APEC%20leaders%2C%20including%20from%20Canada's%20PM%20Trudeau%20and%20China's%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Goyal%20will%20also%20interact%20with%20eminent%20businesspeople%20and%20industry%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20the%20US-India%20Strategic%20Partnership%20Forum%20(USISPF)%2C%20Dr%20Mukesh%20Aghi%2C%20speaking%20on%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20this%20is%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%20for%20Prosperity%20(IPEF)%20and%20APEC.%20USISPF%20in%20an%20event%20will%20be%20bringing%20in%20US%20technology%20companies%2C%20from%20Al%20to%20chipmaking%20to%20cybersecurity%2C%20and%20exploring%20how%20we%20can%20collaborate%2C%20how%20we%20can%20get%20some%20of%20these%20companies%20to%20come%20and%20invest%20in%20India.%20We're%20also%20looking%20at%20Indian%20startups%20to%20see%20how%20we%20can%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20US.%20So%20it's%20a%20two%20way%20trade%2C%20it's%20a%20two%20way%20transfer%20of%20technology.%20So%20that's%20the%20whole%20objective%20of%20the%20event%20taking%20place%20with%20Minister%20Goyal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%20for%20Prosperity%20(IPEF)%20was%20launched%20jointly%20by%20the%20US%20and%20other%20partner%20countries%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20on%20May%2023%2C%202022%20in%20Tokyo.%20India%20joined%20the%20IPEF%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20attended%20the%20launch%20event%20along%20with%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%2C%20and%20other%20leaders%20from%20partner%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPEF%20seeks%20to%20strengthen%20economic%20engagement%20among%20partner%20countries%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20advancing%20growth%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20framework%20is%20structured%20around%20four%20pillars%20relating%20to%20Trade%20(Pillar%20I)%3B%20Supply%20Chains%20(Pillar%20II)%3B%20a%20clean%20economy%20(Pillar%20III)%3B%20and%20Fair%20Economy%20(Pillar%20IV).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20would%20focus%20on%20strengthening%20economic%20cooperation%20and%20enhancing%20resilience%2C%20sustainability%2C%20inclusiveness%2C%20economic%20growth%2C%20fairness%2C%20and%20competitiveness%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20committed%20to%20a%20free%2C%20open%2C%20and%20inclusive%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20and%20would%20work%20towards%20deepening%20economic%20cooperation%20among%20partners%20for%20the%20growth%20and%20prosperity%20of%20the%20region.%20The%20framework%20is%20inclusive%20and%20allows%20flexibility%20to%20partner%20countries%20to%20associate%20with%20pillars%20based%20on%20their%20respective%20priorities%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20visit%2C%20the%20minister%20would%20interact%20with%20the%20CEOs%20of%20multinationals%2C%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%2C%20the%20startup%20community%2C%20including%20venture%20capitalists%2C%20and%20academia%20to%20propel%20existing%20trade%20and%20investment%20relations%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20US%20business%20communities.%20The%20visit%20would%20focus%20on%20emphasising%20the%20attractiveness%20of%20India%20as%20the%20most%20preferred%20investment%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20will%20hold%20discussions%20on%20the%20need%20and%20potential%20for%20closer%20industrial%20collaborations%2C%20further%20expand%20partnerships%2C%20and%20establish%20trade%20and%20investment%20linkages%20across%20priority%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurated%20interactions%20with%20the%20startup%20ecosystem%20and%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20that%20would%20help%20in%20empowering%20and%20mentoring%20their%20growth%20and%20expansion%20are%20also%20on%20the%20agenda.%20The%20minister%20will%20also%20launch%20the%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accounts%20of%20India's%20(ICAI)%20two%20representative%20offices%20in%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20is%20expected%20to%20interact%20with%20globally%20renowned%20technology%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20academic%20communities%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20specifically%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20to%20undertake%20focused%20discussions%20with%20American%20companies%20looking%20to%20invest%20or%20expand%20in%20India%20across%20sectors%3A%20electronics%20(including%20semiconductors)%2C%20technology%2C%20fintech%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699622940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fjc2nlbvg_elon-musk_625x300_06_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-teslas-india-foray-piyush-goyal-to-meet-elon-musk-report-4563846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Commerce%20and%20Industries%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20is%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20the%20US%20from%20November%2013-17%20to%20attend%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%20(IPEF)%20ministerial%20meeting%20and%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20attend%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20Summit%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-teslas-india-foray-piyush-goyal-to-meet-elon-musk-report-4563846%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-teslas-india-foray-piyush-goyal-to-meet-elon-musk-report-4563846%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-teslas-india-foray-piyush-goyal-to-meet-elon-musk-report-4563846%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lahore%20shuts%20down%20as%20South%20Asian%20cities%20shrouded%20in%20h