Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F18-year-old-college-student-in-us-dies-after-being-hit-by-a-stray-bullet-4564629%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F18-year-old-college-student-in-us-dies-after-being-hit-by-a-stray-bullet-4564629%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Just%20Arrest%2C%20They're%20Planning...%26quot%3B%3A%20AAP%20MP's%20Big%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20arrested%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20made%20a%20huge%20claim%20about%20his%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20%26quot%3BA%20big%20conspiracy%20is%20being%20devised%20to%20frame%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%26quot%3B%20claimed%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20flanked%20by%20several%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20just%20arrest%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20a%20big%20move%20against%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20MP%20indirectly%20targeted%20the%20Centre%20which%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%20claim%20is%20allegedly%20misusing%20probe%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh's%20judicial%20custody%20has%20been%20extended%20till%20November%2024%20by%20a%20Delhi%20court.%20Special%20Judge%20M%20K%20Nagpal%20also%20allowed%20Mr%C2%A0%20Singh%20to%20sign%20some%20documents%20related%20to%20development%20work%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20agency%20on%20October%204%20after%20an%20hours-long%20raid%20at%20his%20home.%20He%20is%20the%20third%20AAP%20leader%20to%20be%20arrested%20by%20a%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20him%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20Satyendar%20Jain%20was%20arrested%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20also%20summoned%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20last%20week%20in%20connec