ts-13004588%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbizarre-mammal-named-after-david-attenborough-and-believed-to-be-extinct-is-rediscovered-by-scientists-13004588%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Rangrez%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09210813%2F11468377596_6d28261f6e_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Rangrez%20(43%2C347%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rangrez%20are%20a%20community%20of%20dyers%20who%20have%20been%20a%20cultural%20symbol%20in%20this%20country.%20They%20have%20their%20own%20unique%20past.%20One%20might%20even%20say%20that%20the%20community%20has%20been%20the%20flag%20bearer%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Ganga-Jamuni%20culture.%20For%20them%2C%20everyone%20is%20equal%20and%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20based%20on%20caste%20or%20religion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20dyed%20and%20stamped%20clothes%2C%20and%20inspired%20classical%20poet%20Amir%20Khusrau%20to%20mention%20it%20in%20his%20famous%20verses%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20have%20snatched%20away%20all%20trace%20of%20me%20with%20just%20one%20glance%E2%80%A6%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%20my%20life%20be%20sacrificed%20for%20you%2C%20o%20my%20cloth-dyer%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20have%20dyed%20me%20in%20your%20colour%20with%20just%20one%20glance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20307px)%2085vw%2C%20307px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22307%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20a%20secular%20India%2C%20this%20song%20of%20Amir%20Khusrau%20evokes%20a%20pleasant%20emotion.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20the%20mechanisation%20of%20the%20textile%20industry%20has%20snatched%20away%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20dyers.%20Culturally%2C%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20caste%20began%20when%20Rangrezi%20came%20to%20be%20divided%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurning%20a%20few%20pages%20in%20history%2C%20one%20can%20see%20the%20golden%20past%20of%20the%20dyers.%20Be%20it%20the%20areas%20of%20Awadh%20or%20the%20era%20of%20Delhi%20Sultanate%20when%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20dyers%20in%20the%20Meena%20Bazaar%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%20was%20no%20less%20than%20that%20of%20any%20Mansabdar.%20Dyers%20also%20dominated%20the%20Rohilkhand%20region%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Varanasi%20was%20no%20less%20than%20their%20home.%20The%20work%20of%20the%20dyers%20on%20Banarasi%20saris%20speaks%20volumes%20even%20today.%20The%20Rangrez%20community%20also%20inhabited%20parts%20of%20Bihar%20and%20West%20Bengal%20and%20some%20areas%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20at%20present%20their%20population%20is%20only%2043%2C347.%20The%20community%20resides%20in%20districts%20like%20Bhagalpur%2C%20Patna%2C%20Nalanda%2C%20Buxar%2C%20etc.%20Since%20it%20is%20quite%20a%20small%20number%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20research%20to%20find%20out%20the%20reason%20behind%20their%20numbers.%20One%20needs%20to%20find%20out%20where%20the%20dyers%20have%20gone%20whose%20shops%20used%20to%20keep%20the%20market%20abuzz.%20Did%20they%20change%20their%20caste%20after%20changing%20professions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERangrez%20are%20mainly%20Muslims.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20Hindu%20Rangrez%20as%20well%2C%20whose%20work%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20Muslim%20Rangrez.%20The%20population%20of%20such%20Rangwa%20people%20is%20only%203%2C001%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20social%20status%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Rangrez%20community%20is%20concerned%2C%20they%20are%20considered%20Sunni%20Muslims%20and%20while%20there%20is%20no%20stigma%20of%20untouchability%20owing%20to%20their%20occupation%2C%20certain%20Ashraf%20Muslims%20look%20down%20upon%20them%2C%20like%20the%20Julahas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20their%20political%20participation%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20in%20Bihar%20is%20only%200.0332%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20and%20in%20the%20current%20democratic%20political%20situation%2C%20this%20number%20casts%20negligible%20influence.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20an%20exaggeration%20to%20say%20that%20this%20community%20or%20caste%20and%20its%20profession%2C%20which%20has%20been%20braving%20significant%20social%2C%20cultural%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20hardships%2C%20is%20on%20its%20last%20leg%20because%20a%20lot%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20world.%20Some%20people%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20keep%20their%20art%20alive.%20But%20when%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20earn%20their%20bread%2C%20how%20long%20will%20they%20survive%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260416%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-rangrejs-the-traditional-dyers%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20series%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260200%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-santarash%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20in%20Urdu%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewireurdu.com%2Fauthor%2Fnaval-kishor-kumar%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699605023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09210813%2F11468377596_6d28261f6e_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-rangrez%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20would%20not%20be%20an%20exaggeration%20to%20say%20that%20this%20community%20or%20caste%20and%20its%20profession%2C%20which%20has%20been%20braving%20significant%20social%2C%20cultural%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20hardships%2C%20is%20on%20its%20last%20leg%20because%20a%20lot%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-rangrez%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'True%20hero'%20NASA%20astronaut%20dies%20aged%2095%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699604340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-frank-borman-nasa_6354719.jpg%3F20231110083529%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrank-borman-nasa-astronaut-dies-aged-95-13004577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Astronaut%20Frank%20Borman%2C%20who%20commanded%20NASA's%20first%20Apollo%20mission%20to%20the%20moon%2C%20has%20died%20aged%2095.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A354%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrank-borman-nasa-astronaut-dies-aged-95-13004577%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrank-borman-nasa-astronaut-dies-aged-95-13004577%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrank-borman-nasa-astronaut-dies-aged-95-13004577%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Exposure%20to%20Air%20Pollution%20Changes%20the%20Way%20Our%20Airways%20Behave%E2%80%99%3A%20Surge%20in%20Respiratory%20Symptoms%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07121500%2Fimage-1480.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20national%20capital%E2%80%99s%20air%20quality%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fstory%2Fdelhi-ncr-pollution-air-quality-index-severe-artificial-rain-2460675-2023-11-09%5C%22%3Ehas%20reached%3C%2Fa%3E%20alarming%20levels%2C%20with%20adverse%20consequences%20not%20only%20on%20public%20health%20but%20also%20on%20the%20economic%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20environment%20minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20on%20November%208%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fstory%2Fdelhi-pollution-minister-gopal-rai-meets-iit-kanpur-team-to-discuss-possibility-of-artificial-rain-2460546-2023-11-08%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ea%20team%20from%20IIT%20Kanpur%20to%20discuss%20the%20possibility%20of%20artificial%20rainfall%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20cloud%20seeding%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20AQI%20(air%20quality%20index)%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20decided%20that%20artificial%20rain%20could%20be%20used%20in%20Delhi%20on%20November%2020-21%20if%20the%20weather%20is%20cloudy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pollution%20crisis%20in%20Delhi%20is%20primarily%20attributed%20to%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20industrial%20activities%2C%20and%20crop%20burning%20in%20neighboring%20states.%20The%20concentration%20of%20harmful%20pollutants%20such%20as%20PM2.5%20and%20PM10%20particles%20has%20surged%2C%20leading%20to%20respiratory%20issues%2C%20cardiovascular%20problems%2C%20and%20a%20general%20decline%20in%20the%20overall%20well-being%20of%20the%20populace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntense%20air%20pollution%20exposure%20is%20changing%20the%20way%20our%20airways%20behave%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20healthy%20people%20have%20also%20complained%20of%20the%20new%20onset%20symptom%20of%20cough%2C%20breathlessness%2C%20chest%20tightness%2C%20fatigue%2C%20headache%2C%20eye%20irritation%2C%20and%20sneezing.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20something%20new.%20This%20is%20what%20we%20see%20during%20this%20season.%20We%20have%20been%20seeing%20it%20for%20the%20last%20many%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Karan%20Madan%2C%20additional%20professor%2C%20Department%20of%20Pulmonary%2C%20Critical%20Care%20and%20Sleep%20Medicine%2C%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20we%20see%20these%20symptoms%20when%20air%20quality%20goes%20down%20does%20tend%20to%20point%20out%20that%20these%20symptoms%20are%20related%20to%20worsening%20air%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20we%20can%20attribute%20these%20symptoms%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHealthy%20people%20get%20cough%2C%20hacking%20cough%2C%20allergies.%20We%20treat%20them%20just%20the%20way%20we%20treat%20asthma.%20Asthma%20is%20an%20allergic%20condition.%20Those%20healthy%20people%20who%20develop%20these%20symptoms%2C%20and%20are%20responding%20to%20inhaled%20steroids%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20incorrect%20to%20say%20that%20%5Bair%20pollution%5D%20is%20triggering%20asthma-like%20conditions%20or%20probably%20allergic%20conditions%20in%20healthy%20people.%20Many%20times%20their%20hacking%20cough%20also%20requires%20some%20treatments%20with%20steroids.%20It%20does%20mean%20that%20this%20intense%20air%20pollution%20exposure%20makes%20some%20changes%20in%20the%20way%20our%20airways%20behave%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20respiratory%20illnesses%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20consistently%20noticing%20for%20the%20last%20many%20years%20that%20when%20viral%20infection%20is%20going%20on%2C%20we%20know%20that.%20But%20during%20these%20episodes%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%20viral%2C%20which%20is%20cause%20of%20the%20exacerbation.%20When%20the%20air%20quality%20goes%20down%2C%20many%20people%20start%20complaining%20of%20these%20acute%20respiratory%20symptoms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20heart%20patients%2C%20it%20may%20be%20more%20harmful.%20There%20are%20studies%20to%20show%20that%20air%20pollution%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20BP%3B%20hypertension%20increases.%20An%20increase%20in%20BP%20is%20not%20good%20for%20any%20heart%20patient.%20Data%20says%20very%20poor%20air%20quality%20is%20not%20good%20for%20patients%20with%20cardiac%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20patients%20with%20airway%20diseases%2C%20such%20as%20asthma%20and%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%20(COPD)%2C%20who%20are%20under%20the%20hospital%20follow-up%2C%20have%20reported%20a%20notable%20deterioration%20in%20their%20symptoms.%20Complaints%20include%20increased%20wheeziness%2C%20heightened%20breathlessness%2C%20and%20a%20greater%20need%20for%20inhalers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20severity%20has%20escalated%20to%20acute%20asthma%20attacks%2C%20leading%20to%20hospitalizations%20and%20necessitating%20intensified%20treatments%2C%20including%20the%20administration%20of%20oral%20steroids.%20The%20overall%20frequency%20of%20asthma%20exacerbations%20or%20attacks%20has%20shown%20a%20notable%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20have%20had%20acute%20asthma%20attacks%2C%20some%20of%20which%20required%20hospitalisations%2C%20and%20some%20have%20required%20escalation%20of%20their%20treatments.%20We%20had%20to%20give%20them%20oral%20steroids.%20Asthma%20exacerbation%20or%20attacks%20have%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20AIIMS%20director%20and%20senior%20pulmonologist%20Dr.%20Randeep%20Guleria%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsevere-plus-air-leading-to-more-breathing-problems-ex-aiims-director-explains-101699270128237.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20people%20with%20no%20respiratory%20diseases%20are%20also%20facing%20breathing%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRespiratory%20problems%20may%20increase%20in%20people%20with%20diseases%20like%20bronchitis%20or%20heart%20problems%2C%20resulting%20in%20decreased%20oxygen%20saturation%20and%20increased%20emergency%20visits.%20In%20OPD%20too%2C%20more%20patients%20with%20a%20complaint%20of%20breathing%20are%20coming.%20Hospitalisation%2C%20ICU%20admissions%2C%20and%20OPD%20referrals%20are%20increasing%20in%20patients%20and%20also%20in%20those%20people%20who%20are%20normal%20and%20have%20no%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Guleria%20told%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-working-class-stays-outdoors-despite-health-issues-sees-a-cut-in-pay%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Air%20Pollution%3A%20Working%20Class%20Stays%20Outdoors%20Despite%20Health%20Issues%2C%20Sees%20a%20Cut%20in%20Pay%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20the%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20is%20the%20second%20biggest%20factor%20affecting%20human%20health%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Air%20Quality%20Report%202022%2C%20prepared%20by%20Swiss%20organisation%20IQAir.%20The%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fair-pollution-health-risk-india-annual-economic-cost-over-usd-150-billion-1928843-2022-03-24%5C%22%3Ewas%20released%3C%2Fa%3E%20globally%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20the%20problem%20of%20air%20pollution%20costs%20the%20Indian%20economy%20%2495%20billion%20per%20year.%20Therefore%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20need%20to%20reduce%20air%20pollution%20to%20increase%20economic%20growth.%3Cb%3E%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20if%20India%20had%20achieved%20safe%20air%20quality%20levels%20in%202019%2C%20its%20GDP%20would%20have%20increased%20by%20%2495%20billion%2C%20or%203%25%2C%20as%20Indian%20businesses%20would%20face%20lower%20costs%20and%20higher%20revenues.%20This%20means%20there%20was%20potential%20to%20return%20a%20value%20equal%20to%2050%25%20of%20all%20tax%20collected%20annually%2C%20or%20150%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20budget.%20Bringing%20clean%20air%20to%20India%20benefits%20the%20economy%20and%20businesses%20through%20lower%20absenteeism%2C%20higher%20on-the-job%20productivity%2C%20higher%20consumer%20footfall%20and%20lower%20premature%20mortality%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2021%2F06%2Fair-pollution-india-economy-business%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699601400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07121500%2Fimage-1480.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fexposure-to-air-pollution-changes-the-way-our-airways-behave-surge-in-respiratory-symptoms-in-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apart%20from%20the%20detrimental%20health%20impact%2C%20the%20economic%20toll%20of%20air%20pollution%20on%20India%20is%20staggering.%20The%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20estimates%20an%20annual%20cost%20of%20%2495%20billion%2C%20or%203%25%20of%20India's%20GDP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fexposure-to-air-pollution-changes-the-way-our-airways-behave-surge-in-respiratory-symptoms-in-del