0was%2C%20with%20much%20fanfare%20and%20joy%2C%20taken%20into%20the%20BJP%20and%20on%20that%20occasion%2C%20Union%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20distributed%20sweets%20and%20welcomed%20Malinga%20by%20feeding%20him%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bhanwar%20Meghwanshi%2C%20author%20and%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20Dalit%20violence%20an%20election%20issue%2C%20putting%20up%20posters%20everywhere%20with%20the%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%98Rajasthan%20will%20not%20tolerate%20Dalit%20atrocities%2C%20BJP%20is%20the%20solution%2C%E2%80%99%20while%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20is%20promoting%20a%20man%20who%20has%20committed%20a%20gruesome%20attack%20on%20a%20Dalit.%20This%20has%20exposed%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20several%20Dalit%20groups%20across%20the%20state%20came%20together%20to%20form%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%2C%20called%20%3Cem%3EAnusuchit%20Jaati%20Adhikar%20Abhiyaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20From%20August%2019%20to%20September%2016%2C%20the%20Abhiyaan%20held%20dialogues%20across%20the%20state%20which%20culminated%20with%20a%20Dalit%20manifesto%20released%20on%20September%2028.%20In%20both%20the%20dialogues%20and%20the%20manifesto%2C%20a%20key%20demand%20is%20to%20deny%20a%20ticket%20to%20anyone%20accused%20of%20Dalit%20atrocities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20heard%20our%20demand%20and%20denied%20candidature%20to%20Malinga%2C%20even%20though%20it%20may%20hurt%20them%20electorally.%20We%20welcomed%20their%20principled%20stand%20but%20are%20outraged%20by%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Meghwanshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20letter%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A