ister-and-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20ITLF-MHA%20Second%20Meeting%20Addresses%20Burial%20Site%20Conflict%20Between%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20Communities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09225411%2Fimage-1493.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20November%209%20(Thursday)%2C%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20met%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%E2%80%99s%20objective%20was%20to%20evaluate%20the%20previous%20session%20with%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20on%20August%208%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20which%20had%20focused%20on%20the%20burial%20site%20issue%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20burial%20issue%20goes%20back%20to%20August%203%2C%20when%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20sought%20to%20bury%20their%20fellow%20members%2C%20who%20had%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20violence%20began%20on%20May%203%2C%20in%20an%20open%20field%20in%20S.%20Boljang%20village%2C%20which%2C%20as%20per%20their%20claim%2C%20falls%20within%20the%20Churachandpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20said%20that%20the%20area%20belonged%20to%20the%20Meitei-dominating%20Bishnupur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20a%20burial%20by%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20on%20August%203%20heightened%20tensions%20at%20the%20border%2C%20resulting%20in%20hundreds%20of%20men%20from%20both%20communities%20gathering%20at%20the%20Bishnupur-Churachandpur%20border.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20intervened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20meeting%20between%20ITLF%20and%20MHA.%20As%20earlier%20mentioned%2C%20the%20first%20meeting%20happened%20on%20August%208%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20issues%20were%20discussed%20in%20the%20meeting%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20ITLF%20addressed%20the%20breach%20of%20their%20agreement%20regarding%20the%20State%20commando%20in%20Moreh.%20It%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20the%20complete%20removal%20of%20state%20forces%20from%20hill%20areas.%20Although%20the%20ministry%20asserted%20the%20inability%20to%20entirely%20withdraw%20state%20forces%2C%20a%20commitment%20was%20made%20to%20prevent%20independent%20state%20force%20actions%20in%20hill%20areas.%20Acknowledging%20a%20lapse%20in%20Moreh%2C%20the%20government%20assured%20that%20such%20incidents%20would%20be%20avoided%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20In%20terms%20of%20political%20demands%2C%20interlocutor%20A.K.%20Mishra%20highlighted%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20group%E2%80%99s%20pending%20demands%20awaiting%20government%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20there%20are%20around%2030%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20with%2025%20engaged%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-politics%2Fwhat-is-the-soo-agreement-manipur-govt-withdrew-from-8494829%2F%5C%22%3Etripartite%20SoO%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20state.%20Among%20them%2C%2017%20fall%20under%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organisation%20(KNO)%2C%20and%20eight%20are%20part%20of%20the%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(UPF).%20The%20SoO%20pact%2C%20initiated%20on%20August%2022%2C%202008%2C%20aims%20to%20facilitate%20political%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20advocating%20for%20a%20separate%20Kuki%20state%2C%20the%20groups%20have%20now%20scaled%20down%20their%20demands%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98Kukiland%20territorial%20council%E2%80%99%20with%20financial%20and%20administrative%20autonomy%20from%20the%20Manipur%20Assembly%20and%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Mishra%20also%20urged%20ITLF%20to%20refrain%20from%20resorting%20to%20violent%20means.%20While%20ITLF%20leaders%20expressed%20their%20desire%20for%20peace%2C%20they%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20defend%20themselves%20when%20provoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20ITLF%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20selective%20justice%20by%20the%20National%20Investigative%20Agency%20and%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20saying%20that%20some%20gruesome%20cases%20were%20not%20taken%20up%20by%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20government%20assured%20that%20justice%20would%20be%20pursued%20in%20these%20cases%20with%20the%20CBI%20and%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20ITLF%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20the%20release%20and%20transfer%20of%20minor%20cases%20among%20jail%20inmates.%20It%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20expedite%20the%20process%20for%20the%20remaining%20inmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20It%20voiced%20concerns%20about%20the%20thousands%20of%20looted%20arms%20in%20civilian%20hands.%20To%20this%2C%20MHA%20leaders%20assured%20efforts%20to%20collect%20these%20arms%20and%20emphasised%20on%20the%20need%20for%20a%20similar%20initiative%20in%20Churachandpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20meeting%20reached%20a%20deadlock%2C%20but%20there%20are%20plans%20to%20reconvene%20the%20meeting%20tomorrow%20(November%2010).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20in%20Manipur%2C%20violence%20has%20persisted%20for%20over%20six%20months%2C%20and%20more%20than%20200%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699550789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09225411%2Fimage-1493.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-itlf-mha-second-meeting-addresses-burial-site-conflict-between-kuki-and-meitei-communities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20meeting%20reached%20a%20deadlock%2C%20but%20there%20are%20plans%20to%20reconvene%20the%20meeting%20on%20November%2010.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-itlf-mha-second-meeting-addresses-burial-site-conflict-between-kuki-and-meitei-communities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Rejects%20Australian%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Jurisdiction%20in%20Judgment%20Against%20Former%20Indian%20Diplomat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09221829%2F272741300_300937185402961_3315864555464272419_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20rejected%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20an%20Australian%20court%20over%20its%20ex-parte%20direction%20to%20its%20former%20high%20commissioner%20to%20pay%20a%20penalty%20to%20an%20Indian%20staff%20member%20for%20violating%20local%20wage%20standards%20and%20announced%20plans%20on%20Thursday%2C%20November%209%2C%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20with%20Australian%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%203%2C%20an%20Australian%20federal%20court%20ordered%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Canberra%20Navdeep%20Singh%20Suri%20to%20pay%20A%24136%2C000%20to%20a%20former%20staff%20member%20employed%20at%20the%20official%20residence%20for%20not%20paying%20her%20as%20per%20Australia%E2%80%99s%202009%20Fair%20Work%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Faustralia-domestic-help-high-commissioner%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%20earlier%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20judgment%20on%20diplomatic%20privileges%20and%20immunities%2C%20since%20the%20complainant%20Seema%20Shergill%20had%20been%20in%20Australia%20with%20an%20official%20passport%20with%20a%20diplomatic%20visa%20during%20the%20period%20of%20the%20dispute.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20first%20response%20from%20India%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20New%20Delhi%20%E2%80%9Creject%5Bs%5D%20any%20locus%20standi%20of%20Australian%20authorities%20to%20adjudicate%20on%20matters%20concerning%20such%20India-based%20Service%20Staff%20of%20the%20High%20Commission%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20up%20the%20matter%E2%80%9D%20with%20Australia%2C%20Bagchi%20urged%20Canberra%20%E2%80%9Cto%20uphold%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%2C%20particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20diplomatic%20immunities%20and%20privileges%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeema%20Shergill%20had%20travelled%20with%20Suri%20as%20India-based%20service%20staff%20in%202015.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20she%20left%20the%20official%20residence%2C%20known%20as%20India%20House%2C%20without%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20claimed%20that%20Shergill%20had%20%E2%80%9Cwillfully%20deserted%20her%20post%20in%20May%202016%2C%20a%20day%20before%20her%20scheduled%20return%20to%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20repeatedly%20requested%20Australian%20authorities%20to%20locate%20and%20repatriate%20her%20to%20India.%20We%20have%20learnt%20that%20she%20has%20made%20allegations%20against%20the%20then%20High%20Commissioner%2C%20and%20an%20ex-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparte%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment%20has%20now%20been%20issued%20by%20an%20Australian%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPointing%20out%20that%20she%20was%20an%20India-based%20service%20staff%20at%20the%20diplomatic%20mission%2C%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20asserted%20that%20any%20grievance%20had%20to%20be%20redressed%20only%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20conduct%20and%20false%20representations%20give%20rise%20to%20suspicions%20that%20all%20this%20has%20been%20motivated%20by%20her%20desire%20to%20permanently%20stay%20in%20Australia%2C%20and%20in%20which%20she%20seems%20to%20have%20succeeded.%20We%20are%20also%20concerned%20by%20the%20ex-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eparte%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20court%20judgment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Shergill%20declined%20to%20sign%20a%20compulsory%20undertaking%20in%20May%202016%20committing%20to%20return%20to%20India%20after%20completing%20a%20three-year%20tenure%20%E2%80%93%20a%20provision%20introduced%20in%20response%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Faustralia-domestic-help-high-commissioner%5C%22%3EKhobragade%20affair%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESources%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20diplomats%20and%20staff%20receive%20salaries%20according%20to%20Indian%20scales.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20were%20concerns%20that%20the%20ruling%20might%20prompt%20service%20staff%20in%20Indian%20missions%20abroad%20to%20pursue%20compensation%20under%20local%20laws%20and%20potentially%20persuade%20them%20to%20use%20this%20as%20a%20path%20towards%20citizenship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699548931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09221829%2F272741300_300937185402961_3315864555464272419_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-rejects-australian-courts-jurisdiction-in-judgment-against-former-indian-diplomat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20former%20high%20commissioner%20was%20asked%20to%20pay%20a%20penalty%20to%20an%20Indian%20staff%20member%20for%20violating%20local%20wage%20standards%2C%20New%20Delhi%20announced%20plans%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20with%20Australian%20authorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-rejects-australian-courts-jurisdiction-in-judgment-against-former-indian-diplomat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chhattisgarh%20Polls%3A%20Farmers'%20Votes%20at%20Centre%20of%20Politics%20on%20Paddy%20Prices%2C%20Loan%20Waivers%2C%20Development%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F18131323%2F2285241955_27e5da6d80_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Tolesh%20Kumar%20Chandel%2C%2040%2C%20who%20grows%20paddy%20on%20his%20approximately%20two%20acre%20land%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Narayanpur%20district%2C%20is%20pinning%20his%20hopes%20on%20the%20Congress%20to%20deliver%20its%20promise%20of%20procuring%20paddy%20for%20Rs%203%2C200%20per%20quintal%2C%20if%20it%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20again%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%201.22%20lakh%20which%20was%20waived%20off%20when%20the%20Congress%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202018.%20This%20happened%20after%20it%20had%20promised%20loan%20waivers.%20During%20the%20BJP%20government%20(before%202018)%2C%20we%20used%20to%20get%20Rs%201%2C700%20for%20paddy%20procurement.%20Last%20year%2C%20they%20%5BCongress%20government%5D%20procured%20paddy%20for%20Rs%202%2C500%2C%20and%20this%20year%20we%20have%20got%20Rs%202%2C640.%20If%20they%20(Congress)%20are%20making%20promises%20to%20farmers%2C%20they%20are%20delivering%20on%20it%20as%20well.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20if%20they%20form%20the%20government%20again%2C%20they%20will%20deliver%20on%20their%20promises%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20considered%20as%20the%20rice%20bowl%20of%20India%2C%20poll%20promises%20to%20farmers%2C%20including%20farm%20loan%20waivers%2C%20and%20competitive%20politics%20over%20the%20price%20of%20paddy%20between%20the%20incumbent%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20pivot%20that%20could%20decide%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20that%20ended%2015%20years%20of%20the%20BJP%20rule%20in%20the%20state%2C%20disenchantment%20among%20paddy%20farmers%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20key%20factors%20along%20with%20anti-incumbency%20that%20helped%20the%20Congress%20dislodge%20the%20saffron%20party%20and%20win%2068%20of%20the%2090%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%202018%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20announced%20a%20slew%20of%20promises%20to%20farmers.%20After%20its%20victory%2C%20it%20delivered%20on%20procuring%20paddy%20at%20Rs%20600%20per%20quintal%2C%20which%20is%20above%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20mandated%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%2C%20along%20with%20short-term%20loan%20farm%20loan%20waivers.%20It%20also%20delivered%20on%20providing%20electricity%20up%20to%20400%20units%20at%20half%20the%20rate%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20two-phased%20election%20being%20held%20this%20month%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20once%20again%20pinning%20its%20hopes%20on%20its%20winning%20formula%20of%20farm%20loan%20waivers%20and%20increased%20paddy%20procurement%20prices%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-ts-singh-deo-bhupesh-baghel-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Edeputy%20chief%20minister%20T.S.%20Singh%20Deo%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20be%20going%20to%20the%20voters%20with%20the%20promises%20that%20they%20had%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNowhere%20in%20the%20country%20are%20paddy%20farmers%20getting%20as%20much%20value%20for%20their%20crops%20as%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20We%20had%20assured%20that%20we%20would%20be%20waiving%20short-term%20farm%20loans%2C%20which%20we%20did%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20about%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20assured%20the%20farmers%20that%20we%20would%20purchase%20paddy%20at%20least%20at%20Rs%202%2C500%2Fquintal.%20And%20now%20we%20will%20be%20purchasing%20paddy%20at%20just%20short%20of%20Rs%202%2C800%20in%20November%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20centred%20its%20campaign%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-chhattisgarh-election-raman-singh-bjp-chief-minister-face%5C%22%3Ecorruption%20by%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20learning%20from%20its%20mistake%20in%20the%202018%20defeat%2C%20it%20is%20also%20attempting%20to%20woo%20farmers%20this%20time.%20The%20party%20in%20its%20manifesto%20released%20on%20November%203%20has%20promised%20to%20procure%20paddy%20at%20Rs%203%2C100%20per%20quintal%20(21%20quintal%20per%20acre)%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%20500%20more%20than%20what%20the%20current%20Congress%20government%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20sought%20to%20course%20correct%20on%20its%202013%20promise%20of%20providing%20Rs%20300%20as%20bonus%20per%20quintal%20over%20the%20Centre-mandated%20MSP.%20While%20the%20bonus%20was%20delivered%20in%20the%20first%20three%20years%20of%20the%20Raman%20Singh%20government%2C%20it%20was%20stopped%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Frice-procurement-from-chhattisgarh-restricted-at-24-lakh-mt-centre-7131709%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20Union%20government%20directed%20states%20to%20stop%20giving%20bonuses%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20paddy%20and%20wheat%20procurement%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20the%20party%20in%20its%20manifesto%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20outstanding%20paddy%20procurement%20bonus%20for%20those%20two%20remaining%20years%20at%20Rs%20300%20per%20quintal%20by%20December%2025%2C%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20called%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-bjps-manifesto-a-copy-of-congress-guarantees-claims-cm-baghel%2F682876.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccopy%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20its%20promises%2C%20just%20two%20days%20later%20in%20its%20own%20poll%20manifesto%20released%20on%20November%205%2C%20the%20Congress%20subsequently%20upped%20the%20ante%20and%20promised%20to%20procure%20paddy%20at%20Rs%203%2C200%20(20%20quintal%20per%20acre).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20it%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20once%20again%20waive%20farm%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%2C%2050%2C%20another%20farmer%20in%20Narayanpur%2C%20said%20that%20while%20he%20had%20his%20farm%20loan%20of%20around%20Rs%201%20lakh%20waived%20in%202018%2C%20the%20competitive%20politics%20over%20the%20procurement%20of%20paddy%20prices%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20election%20ploy%20by%20the%20two%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJanta%20ko%20idhar%20udhar%20kar%20rahe%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(They%20are%20trying%20to%20pull%20the%20voters%20from%20one%20side%20to%20the%20other)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENilkanth%20Nag%2C%2052%2C%20in%20Narayanpur%20said%20that%20although%20he%20had%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%202.03%20lakh%20which%20was%20waived%20in%202018%2C%20the%20competitive%20prices%20for%20paddy%20are%20being%20offered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20votes%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20parties%20are%20offering%20higher%20rates%20(for%20paddy).%20The%20current%20rate%20is%20fine.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20increasing%20it%20further%3F%20We%20should%20get%20as%20much%20as%20we%20have%20worked%20for.%20Both%20the%20parties%20are%20doing%20this%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20votes.%20Our%20vote%20is%20for%20development%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20in%20which%20Modi%20has%20done%20good%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Yadav%2C%2027%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Dantewada%20district%2C%20said%20that%20while%20he%20has%20received%20the%20bonus%20and%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20done%20the%20work%20for%20the%20farmers%2C%20development%20still%20remains%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20done%20the%20work.%20But%20we%20need%20more%20schools%2C%20quality%20education.%20The%20main%20concern%20is%20unemployment%2C%20which%20they%20should%20address%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-numbers-poll-congress-bjp-operation-lotus%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%3A%20To%20Remain%20Impervious%20to%20a%20Future%20Operation%20Lotus%2C%20Can%20Congress%20Pull%20off%20a%20Big%20Victory%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Farmers%20will%20decide%20the%20elections%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudesh%20Tikam%2C%20a%20Rajnandgaon-based%20farmer%20leader%2C%20who%20had%20also%20contested%20the%202019%20elections%20as%20an%20independent%2C%20said%20that%20the%20competitive%20politics%20over%20procurement%20prices%20for%20farmers%20highlights%20the%20success%20of%20bringing%20in%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20to%20the%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20disenchantment%20against%20the%20Raman%20Singh%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20fulfill%20its%20promise%20of%20providing%20the%20outstanding%20bonus%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory.%20The%20contrasting%20poll%20promises%20regarding%20paddy%20procurement%20by%20both%20parties%20now%20underscore%20the%20triumph%20of%20the%20kisan%20andolan%20in%20the%20state%2C%20successfully%20bringing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20to%20the%20mainstream%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20both%20the%20parties%20are%20pledging%20paddy%20procurement%20above%20Rs%203%2C000%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20an%20edge%20over%20the%20BJP%20in%20this%20election%20because%20of%20a%20trust%20deficit%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20marks%20a%20big%20victory%20for%20the%20farmers%20as%20a%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20that%20was%20initially%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20bonus%20over%20MSP%20prices%2C%20is%20now%20offering%20them%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20only%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20manifestos%20is%20the%20promise%20of%20farm%20loan%20waivers.%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20promising%20any%20loan%20waivers.%20It%20is%2C%20however%2C%20promising%20to%20give%20the%20outstanding%20bonus%20that%20was%20left%20over%20from%20its%20last%20two%20years%20in%20power.%20There%20is%20a%20trust%20issue%20involved%20here.%20When%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%2C%20it%20had%20promised%20to%20give%20a%20Rs%20300%20bonus%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20give%20it%20for%20the%20full%20five%20years.%20So%2C%20in%20that%20sense%20it%20is%20behind%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20delivered%20on%20its%20promise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20previous%20election%2C%20even%20farmers%20affiliated%20to%20the%20BJP%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress.%20The%20course%20correction%20is%20visible%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20manifesto.%20But%20the%20trust%20issue%20remains.%20How%20farmers%20will%20react%20to%20this%2C%20only%20time%20will%20tell%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikam%20added%20that%20either%20way%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20will%20decide%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20will%20decide%20not%20only%20this%20election%20but%20the%20next%20few%20elections%20as%20well.%20Farmers%20will%20only%20decide%20who%20will%20form%20the%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-rajasthan-madhya-pradesh-mizoram-telangana-election%5C%22%3EAs%20Five%20States%20Go%20to%20the%20Polls%2C%20the%20Power%20of%20the%20Poor%20Will%20Decide%20the%20Results%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Paddy%20procurement%20not%20a%20decisive%20electoral%20issue%20anymore%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Neeraj%20Mishra%2C%20a%20Raipur-based%20political%20commentator%20and%20senior%20journalist%2C%20while%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20remain%20important%2C%20paddy%20procurement%20and%20loan%20waivers%20on%20their%20own%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20as%20decisive%20an%20election%20issue%20as%20it%20was%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20electoral%20terms%2C%20it%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20whether%20you%20will%20give%20Rs%203%2C100%20or%20Rs%203%2C200.%20The%20farmers%20are%20happy%20because%20they%20are%20getting%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%202%2C600%20anyway.%20They%20%5Bpolitical%20parties%5D%20can%20give%20more%20but%20they%20will%20not%20give%20less.%20That%20is%20their%20%5Bfarmers%E2%80%99%5D%20assumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issue%20is%20a%20big%20factor.%20So%2C%20this%20time%20the%20BJP%20had%20to%20fall%20in%20line%20%5Bwith%20the%20promises%20made%20to%20farmers%5D.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20it%20will%20be%20a%20much%20closer%20election%20than%202018%20as%20voters%20will%20return%20to%20voting%20for%20the%20parties%20they%20have%20traditionally%20supported.%20Congress%20may%20still%20win%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20much%20closer%20than%20it%20was%20last%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20feasibility%20of%20poll%20promises%20from%20a%20budgetary%20perspective%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mishra%2C%20the%20feasibility%20of%20poll%20promises%20may%20not%20make%20budgetary%20sense%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sum%20of%20Rs%20500%20that%20is%20being%20given%20as%20a%20bonus%20over%20the%20MSP%20is%20costing%20the%20state%20exchequer%20about%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore.%20Now%20to%20that%20if%20you%20add%20another%20Rs%20500%2C%20then%20it%20will%20add%20another%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer.%20The%20government%20is%20taking%20a%20loan%20to%20pay%20this.%20About%2066%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20loan%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20is%20because%20of%20this.%20The%20farmer%20does%20not%20care%20where%20this%20money%20is%20coming%20from.%20But%20this%20will%20add%20to%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20farm%20loan%20waivers%2C%20Mishra%20mentioned%20that%20despite%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20in%20waiving%20farm%20loans%2C%20there%20remains%20an%20outstanding%20amount%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2016%2C000%20crore%20yet%20to%20be%20waived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20post-procurement%20issues%20need%20to%20be%20considered%2C%20including%20the%20adverse%20impact%20on%20other%20infrastructure%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bonus%20is%20being%20paid%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20other%20infrastructure.%20It%20(the%20Congress%20government)%20has%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20all%20other%20development%20work%20like%20roads%20and%20other%20infrastructure.%20Paddy%20is%20getting%20wasted%20when%20stored%20in%20open%20skies%2C%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20infrastructure%20to%20store%20it.%20There%20is%20still%20remaining%20stock%20from%20last%20year.%20Where%20will%20you%20keep%20all%20this%3F%20What%20will%20happen%20after%20another%20five%20years%3F%20Infrastructure%20has%20not%20been%20developed%20to%20keep%20the%20grains.%20Post%20procurement%20is%20also%20a%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699543834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F18131323%2F2285241955_27e5da6d80_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-farmers-votes-at-centre-of-politics-on-paddy-prices-loan-waivers-development%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20Congress%20is%20banking%20on%20farm%20loan%20waivers%20and%20higher%20paddy%20procurement%20at%20Rs%203%2C200%20per%20quintal%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20aiming%20to%20course%20correct%20from%202018%20with%20a%20promise%20of%20procurement%20at%20Rs%203%2C100%20per%20quintal%20and%20clearing%20the%20outstanding%20bonus%20from%20the%20last%20two%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-farmers-votes-at-centre-of-politics-on-paddy-prices-loan-waivers-development%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Is%20How%20Americans%20Really%20Feel%20About%20Tipping%20%E2%80%94%20And%20Who%20They're%20Likely%20To%20Tip%20Most%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20new%20survey%20shows%20U.S.%20adults%20are%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20tip%20certain%20service%20workers%20than%20others.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699542004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F654bf029220000a81518dce6.jpeg%3Fcache%3DOR5yogO3XL%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Famericans-tipping-habits-poll_n_654befb2e4b0e63c9dc21556%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20survey%20shows%20U.S.%20adults%20are%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20tip%20certain%20service%20workers%20than%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Famericans-tipping-habits-poll_n_654befb2e4b0e63c9dc21556%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Famericans-tipping-habits-poll_n_654befb2e4b0e6