0will%20find%20more%20ways%20to%20use%20the%20survey%E2%80%99s%20results%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20be%20glad%20if%20the%20%5BUnion%20government%5D%20too%20agrees%20to%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20%5Bhikes%5D%20reservations%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20added%2C%20according%20to%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bihar%20unit%20extended%20its%20support%20for%20the%20increase%20in%20legislation%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpatna%2Fafter-amit-shah-sushil-modi-asks-nitish-how-numbers-of-some-obcs-and-upper-castes-have-come-down-since-1931-9016395%2F%5C%22%3Eunit%20chief%20Sushil%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Famit-shah-bihar-caste-survey-yadav-muslim%5C%22%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20alleged%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20survey%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-assembly-clears-bill-to-hike-reservation-nitish-kumar-caste-survey-101699521752737.html%5C%22%3EKumar%20has%20responded%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20say%20their%20caste%20numbers%20have%20come%20down%20or%20some%20castes%20have%20inflated%20figures%20are%20talking%20trash.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20caste%20survey%20after%201931.%20How%20do%20they%20know%20their%20numbers%20without%20any%20study%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20survey%20also%20sought%20to%20measure%20the%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20about%2094%20lakh%20families%20%E2%80%93%20or%2034.13%25%20of%20the%20total%202.76%20crore%20families%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20are%20economically%20poor%20and%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20a%20month.%