%20Delhi%20after%20clearing%20my%20prelims%20to%20give%20an%20interview.%20It%20took%20about%20two%20years%20for%20the%20government%20to%20identify%20a%20suitable%20posting%20for%20me%20due%20to%20my%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20those%20two%20years%20that%20I%20started%20mentoring%20students%20just%20as%20a%20pastime.%20But%20soon%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20teaching%20them%20gave%20me%20happiness.%20Their%20getting%20good%20ranks%20gave%20me%20a%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Chennai%20to%20serve%20my%20time%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defense.%20Even%20while%20working%2C%20I%20would%20give%20guidance%20and%20training%20to%20aspirants.%20They%20would%20live%20with%20me%2C%20and%20I%20would%20mentor%20them.%20Most%20of%20them%20became%20like%20family%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20happy%20working%20as%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20my%20true%20calling%20lay%20in%20teaching.%20In%202014%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20my%20life%20to%20imparting%20my%20knowledge%20and%20helping%20others%20realise%20their%20dreams%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20exam%20once%20again%20and%20refresh%20my%20knowledge.%20I%20got%20an%20AIR%20160%20and%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20start%20my%20own%20coaching%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20returned%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%2018%20years%20of%20pure%20joy%20since.%20I%20have%20lost%20count%20of%20how%20many%20students%20I%20have%20taught%20so%20far.%20I%20teach%20around%202%2C000%20to%203%2C000%20students%20every%20year.%20Of%20those%2C%20around%20100%20have%20realised%20their%20dream%20of%20becoming%20civil%20servants%20and%20are%20serving%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20my%20students%20are%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298557%2Fkerala-