22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09183453%2Fimage-1490.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffintechs-eye-growing-demand-of-affluent-indians-while-rural-demand-sees-sluggish-recovery%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20report%20shows%20a%20substantial%20growth%20opportunity%20for%20fintech%20companies%2C%20highlighting%20the%20burgeoning%20base%20of%20affluent%20individuals%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20free%20ration%20scheme%20has%20been%20extended%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffintechs-eye-growing-demand-of-affluent-indians-while-rural-demand-sees-sluggish-recovery%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Filmmaker%20Sudhanva%20Deshpande%20Accuses%20Times%20Now%20of%20Spreading%20%E2%80%98Misinformation%E2%80%99%20Against%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09171437%2Fimage-1489.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Renowned%20filmmaker%2C%20actor%2C%20and%20author%20Sudhanva%20Deshpande%20on%20November%209%20(Thursday)%20released%20a%20statement%2C%20condemning%20what%20he%20calls%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdisinformation%20campaign%E2%80%9D%20orchestrated%20by%20news%20channel%20Times%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20revolves%20around%20a%20lecture%20held%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Bombay%20(IIT-B)%20on%20November%206%2C%20where%20Deshpande%20was%20invited%20by%20Professor%20Sharmistha%20Saha%20to%20introduce%20the%202004%20documentary%20film%20%3Cem%3EArna%E2%80%99s%20Children%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20directed%20by%20Israeli%20Jewish%20filmmaker%20Juliano%20Mer%20Khamis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20introduction%20to%20the%20documentary%2C%20Deshpande%20was%20invited%20to%20give%20a%20lecture%2C%20which%20certain%20students%20believed%20was%20pro-Hamas%20and%20pro-violence.%20They%20further%20alleged%20glorification%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmilitant%20terrorists%E2%80%9D%20during%20Deshpande%E2%80%99s%20introductory%20lecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20complaint%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20Professor%20Saha%2C%20questioning%20the%20appropriateness%20of%20extending%20the%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Ffilmmaker-sudhanva-deshpande-releases-statement-accusing-times-now-of-spreading-malicious-misinformation-against-him%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESabrang%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Times%20Now%20ran%20a%20programme%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9CIITians%20Allege%20Prof.%20Saha%20for%20Inviting%20Filmmaker%20who%20Glorified%20Palestinian%20Terrorist%E2%80%9D%2C%20on%20November%208%2C%20framing%20Deshpande%20and%20professor%20Saha%20as%20Hamas%20supporters%20and%20apologists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20opened%20with%20the%20following%20statement%3A%20%E2%80%9CMumbai%3A%20Hamas%20Backers%20get%20a%20Stage%E2%80%9D.%20The%20host%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20heart%20of%20the%20Hamas%20backers%20continue%20to%20bleed%2C%20not%20for%20the%20innocents%20butchered%20by%20them%20but%20for%20the%20terrorists%20who%20picked%20up%20arms%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20freedom%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20featured%20clips%20of%20Deshpande%E2%80%99s%20statements%2C%20selectively%20presented%20without%20context.%20Deshpande%E2%80%99s%20recount%20of%20his%202015%20meeting%20with%20Zakaria%20Zubeidi%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Al%20Aqsa%20Martyrs%E2%80%99%20Brigades%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20was%20portrayed%20as%20endorsing%20violence%20and%20terrorism.%20However%2C%20the%20programme%20failed%20to%20provide%20a%20comprehensive%20understanding%20of%20Deshpande%E2%80%99s%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Times%20Now%20reporter%20participates%20in%20the%20show%2C%20asking%20some%20students%20to%20give%20details%20on%20%E2%80%9Chow%20the%20lecture%20was%20pro-Hamas%20and%20how%20two%20militants%20belonging%20to%20Hamas%20were%20glorified%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20responding%20student%20states%20that%20while%20giving%20the%20introduction%20to%20the%20documentary%20being%20screened%2C%20Deshpande%2C%20to%20his%20shock%2C%20agreed%20to%20having%20met%20Zakaria%20and%20also%20called%20him%20a%20legend.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20this%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20attempt%20to%20influence%20the%20students%20of%20IIT-B%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3ESabrang%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20students%20go%20on%20to%20state%20that%20there%20should%20be%20checks%20and%20balances%20in%20premier%20institutes%20such%20as%20IIT-B.%20The%20responding%20student%20also%20accuses%20the%20dean%2C%20director%2C%20deputy%20director%20and%20other%20authorities%20of%20the%20institution%20of%20ignoring%20the%20emails%20sent%20by%20him%20regarding%20the%20aforementioned%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reporter%20interviewed%20another%20student%20standing%20there%2C%20who%20said%20he%20was%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20impugned%20lecture%2C%20but%20added%20that%20there%20should%20be%20zero%20tolerance%20for%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20acts.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Csad%20after%20hearing%20that%20such%20lectures%20were%20being%20given%20in%20the%20campus%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20Vice%20President%20was%20speaking%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20field%20reporter%20of%20Times%20Now%2C%20based%20on%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20two%20students%2C%20then%20deduced%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstudents%20of%20the%20IIT-B%20are%20very%20much%20appalled%20by%20what%20happened%20in%20their%20campus%20and%20they%20were%20not%20expecting.%20It%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20movie%20screening%20before%20which%2C%20out%20of%20the%20blue%2C%20a%20lecture%20was%20given%20which%20is%20pro-Hamas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699533048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09171437%2Fimage-1489.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffilmmaker-sudhanva-deshpande-accuses-times-now-of-spreading-misinformation-against-him%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20matter%20revolves%20around%20a%20lecture%20held%20at%20the%20IIT-B%20on%20November%206%2C%20where%20Deshpande%20was%20invited%20by%20professor%20Sharmistha%20Saha%20to%20give%20a%20lecture%2C%20which%20certain%20students%20believed%20was%20pro-Hamas%20and%20pro-violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffilmmaker-sudhanva-deshpande-accuses-times-now-of-spreading-misinformation-against-him%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Tells%20High%20Courts%20to%20Set%20Up%20Special%20Benches%20for%20Speedy%20Disposal%20of%20Cases%20Against%20MLAs%2C%20MPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F25130155%2FNew-Lok-Sabha.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20directed%20chief%20justices%20of%20high%20courts%20to%20constitute%20special%20benches%20to%20monitor%20and%20ensure%20the%20speedy%20disposal%20of%20criminal%20cases%20pending%20against%20MLAs%20and%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20noting%20that%20it%20cannot%20frame%20uniform%20guidelines%20on%20the%20matter%20across%20the%20country%2C%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20noted%20that%20high%20courts%20can%20do%20so%20in%20their%20respective%20jurisdiction%20by%20invoking%20Article%20227%20of%20the%20constitution.%20The%20particular%20constitutional%20provision%20gives%20high%20courts%20the%20power%20of%20superintendence%20over%20all%20courts%20and%20tribunals%20throughout%20the%20territories%20in%20relation%20to%20which%20it%20exercises%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20refrained%20from%20framing%20guidelines%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20said%20high%20courts%20should%20register%20suo%20motu%20cases%20in%20their%20respective%20jurisdictions%20titled%20%E2%80%98In%20re%3A%20Designated%20courts%20for%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%E2%80%99%20to%20monitor%20the%20early%20disposal%20of%20criminal%20cases%20pending%20against%20lawmakers.%20It%20said%20priority%20should%20be%20accorded%20to%20those%20cases%20which%20entail%20a%20death%20sentence%20or%20life%20imprisonment%20as%20maximum%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20special%20Bench%20may%20list%20the%20matter%20at%20regular%20intervals%20as%20felt%20necessary.%20The%20high%20court%20chief%20justices%20may%20issue%20such%20orders%20and%20directions%20as%20necessary%20for%20expeditious%20and%20effective%20disposal%20of%20the%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20court%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-expedites-criminal-trials-against-mps-mlas-101699509042880.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20said%20that%20high%20courts%20should%20list%20those%20cases%20where%20trials%20have%20been%20stayed%20by%20making%20all%20efforts%20to%20expedite%20the%20trials.%20To%20ensure%20that%20information%20regarding%20the%20trials%20in%20such%20cases%20is%20public%2C%20he%20ordered%20high%20courts%20to%20a%20separate%20tab%20on%20their%20websites%20to%20put%20various%20details%20regarding%20cases%2C%20including%20the%20status%20of%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%20directions%20came%20in%20response%20to%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20advocate%20Ashwini%20Upadhyay%20in%202016%2C%20which%20sought%20directives%20to%20authorities%20concerned%20for%20fast-tracking%20criminal%20trials%20against%20sitting%20and%20former%20MPs%20and%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20senior%20advocate%20Vijay%20Hansaria%2C%20acting%20as%20amicus%20curiae%20in%20the%20case%2C%20trials%20are%20pending%20in%205%2C175%20cases%20across%20the%20country%20in%20which%20MLAs%20and%20MPs%20are%20accused.%20Of%20them%2C%20trial%20in%202%2C116%20cases%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20around%2040%25%2C%20has%20been%20pending%20for%20over%20five%20years%2C%20and%20most%20of%20these%20cases%20are%20from%C2%A0Uttar%20Pradesh%20(1%2C377)%2C%20Bihar%20(546)%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%20(482).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fforty-percent-of-mps-have-criminal-cases-against-them-adr-report-says%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%2C%2040%25%20of%20sitting%20MPs%20have%20declared%20criminal%20cases%20against%20them%2C%20with%2025%25%20of%20legislators%20being%20accused%20of%20serious%20crimes%20including%20murder%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20kidnapping%2C%20and%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadrindia.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnalysis_of_Criminal_Background_Financial_Education_Gender_and_other_details_of_Sitting_MPs_2023_Final_Ver_English.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20and%20New%20Election%20Watch%20(NEW).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699531247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F25130155%2FNew-Lok-Sabha.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-tells-high-courts-to-set-up-special-benches-for-speedy-disposal-of-cases-against-mlas-mps%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20noting%20that%20it%20cannot%20frame%20uniform%20guidelines%20on%20the%20matter%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20high%20courts%20can%20do%20so%20by%20invoking%20Article%20227%20of%20the%20con