har%20Nursing%20Clinic%20in%20Narayangaon%20where%20the%20farmer%20was%20kept%20under%20observation%20for%20three%20days.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20on%20ventilation.%20The%20doctor%20suspected%20that%20he%20might%20be%20bitten%20by%20a%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20viper%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20most%20venomous%20snakes.%20We%20were%20so%20scared%20as%20this%20was%20the%20first%20such%20case%20in%20our%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feared%20that%20the%20venom%20might%20have%20spread%20to%20the%20kidneys%20and%20heart.%20The%20doctor%20had%20performed%20a%20surgery%20to%20remove%20the%20toxins.%20Each%20moment%20was%20difficult%20for%20us.%20But%20the%20surgery%20was%20successful%20and%20my%20father%20was%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%202022%20study%20estimates%20that%20India%20reports%20at%20least%2064%2C000%20snakebite%20deaths%20every%20year%2C%20especially%20making%20people%20living%20in%20the%20rural%20hinterlands%20more%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240