ner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F172628%2Ftelangana-police-hero-snake-rescue-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnake%20encounters%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoften.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Findia%2Fhealth-topics%2Fsnakebite%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSnakebite%2520in%2520India%2C-The%2520World%2520Health%26amp%3Btext%3DPublished%2520reports%2520suggest%2520that%2520between%2Camputations%2520and%2520other%2520permanent%2520disabilities.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E90%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20snakebites%20are%20caused%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98big%20four%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Common%20krait%2C%20Indian%20cobra%2C%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20viper%2C%20and%20the%20Saw%20Scaled%20Viper.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20delay%20in%20administering%20the%20anti-snake%20venom%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20says%2C%20chances%20are%20the%20snake%20bite%20will%20cause%20grave%20organ%20damage%2C%20or%20prove%20to%20be%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20usually%20critically%20ill%20patients%20had%20to%20go%20to%20cities%20for%20treatment%20as%20there%20was%20no%20ambulance%20or%20support%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20many%20would%20die%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Those%20who%20could%20not%20go%20to%20the%20city%20would%20visit%20faith%20healers%20and%20waste%20the%20golden%20hour%20for%20the%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20found%20that%20medical%20officers%20at%20the%20primary%20health%20centres%20would%20be%20reluctant%20to%20treat%20such%20cases%20as%20they%20either%20lacked%20antivenoms%20or%20necessary%20equipment%20such%20as%20ventilator%20support.%20They%20lack%20training%20to%20handle%20such%20emergency%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20started%20equipping%20his%20hospital%20with%20life%20saving%20equipment%20like%20cardiac%20monitors%2C%20ventilators%2C%20and%20oxygen%20cylinders%2C%20so%20that%20he%20could%20save%20lives%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20Over%20the%20past%2028%20years%2C%20his%20efforts%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20mission%20that%20aims%20at%20achieving%20zero%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F78205%2Findiansnakes-jose-louies-snakebites-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnakebite%20deaths%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Dos%20%26amp%3B%20Don%E2%80%99ts%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%20Monsoons%20are%20hectic%20when%20at%20least%2012%20patients%20are%20rushed%20to%20the%20medical%20facility%20in%20a%20day.%20Without%20any%20trained%20medical%20staff%20support%2C%20the%20couple%20works%20round%20the%20clock.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20also%20conducts%20awareness%20programs%20in%20villages%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20forest%20departments%2C%20and%20medical%20colleges.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-150x79.